	(51363,11,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:18',NULL,NULL,'Sampit comes from the city of Sampit and was confiscated after the ethnic war between the Madurais and the Dayaks in this city in February 2001. This gibbon almost died when the house where he lived burned down. In spite of this he loves people, maybe too much, which is why we hesitate to release him back to the wild immediately. He was born in 1998. ','EN'),
