	(51367,12,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:18',NULL,NULL,'Lupah is a small female born in 1998. She comes from western Borneo, and she has been saved by one of the members of the program for the preservation of orangutans working here in Borneo. She is extremely intelligent. Her parents have also been killed  She hopes to recover her freedom thanks to KALAWEIT  \r\n\r\nNow, Lupah has been transfered in the sanctuary in Hampapak island, with her new fellow Tomang. \r\n','EN'),
