	(51529,119,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:18',NULL,NULL,'<p>Bidut est un m&acirc;le gibbon de l\'esp&egrave;ce <em>H</em><em>ylobates </em><em>M</em><em>uelleri muelleri</em>, l\'une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit au sud &ndash; est de Born&eacute;o, approximativement au sud de la rivi&egrave;re Mahakam et &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>L\'estimation de sa naissance : 1994.</p>\r\n<p>Bidut a &eacute;t&eacute; confisque le 24 septembre 2004 a Jakarta.</p>\r\n<p>L\'examen m&eacute;dical&nbsp;: Bidut est sain.</p>\r\n<p>Bidut n\'aime pas l\'homme... parfois il devient agressif quand on est pr&egrave;s de la voli&egrave;re. Bidut saute au grillage pour attraper notre bras ou tee-shirt.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o.</p>\r\n<p>Ao&ucirc;t 2018</p>\r\n<p>Bidut va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec sa compagne Dona.</p>\r\n<p>Ao&ucirc;t 2017</p>\r\n<p>Bidut et sa compagne Dona vont bien. Bidut aime s&rsquo;asseoir en haut de la cage. Parfois il s&rsquo;approche aussi Dona pour jouer.</p>\r\n<p>Le 18 mars 2010&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Bidut et Dona sont transfer&eacute;s vers &nbsp;notre nouveau centre de Pararawen &agrave; Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o centre.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2008</p>\r\n<p>Bidut est maintenant plac&eacute;&nbsp; avec une femelle gibbon qui s\'appelle Dona dans une grande voli&egrave;re de notre refuge qui se trouve sur l\'&icirc;le Hampapak. Bidut et Dona s\'entendent bien.</p>\r\n<p>Ils jouent beaucoup ensemble.</p>\r\n<p>2005</p>\r\n<p>Avant Bidut avait &eacute;t&eacute; avec une autre femelle nomm&eacute;e Rini qui est malheureusement d&eacute;ced&eacute;e &agrave; cause de la&nbsp; pneumonie, le 20 d&eacute;cembre 2005.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(51530,119,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:18',NULL,NULL,'<p><span>Bidut is a male gibbon of&nbsp;<em><span>Hylobates Muelleri muelleri specy,&nbsp;</span></em></span><span>one of gibbons species who liv</span><span>es in southeast Kalimantan, approximately south of the Mahakam river and west of the Barito revier. Indonesia.</span></p>\r\n<p>Year of birth : 1994.</p>\r\n<p>Bidut was confiscated in September, 24 2004 in Jakarta.</p>\r\n<p>Medical review : Bidut is clean.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, &nbsp;Kalimantan Central.</p>\r\n<p>August 2018</p>\r\n<p>Bidut is just fine. He is always with his partner Dona.</p>\r\n<p>Bidut is active and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>January 2016</p>\r\n<p>Bidut and his partner Dona are doing well. Bidut likes to sit on the top of cage. Sometimes he goes towards Dona for to play.</p>\r\n<p>January, 2015</p>\r\n<p>Bidut and his partner are doing well. They are actives. Bidut likes to stay on the top of cage.</p>\r\n<p>Dona likes to go down when there are human close to the cage.</p>\r\n<p>September 2013</p>\r\n<p>Bidut and his partner Dona are fine. They are actives and eat well their food.</p>\r\n<p>Bidut and Done like to play together.</p>\r\n<p>March, 18 2010</p>\r\n<p>Bidut and Dona have been transferred to our new sanctuaire in Pararawen, Muara Teweh, Centre Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>January 2008</p>\r\n<p>Bidut is now with a female gibbon name Dona. They are nice with each other and become friends.</p>\r\n<p>2005</p>\r\n<p>Bidut was with Rini. But sadly, Rini died of pneumonia.</p>','EN'),
