	(51548,75,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:18',NULL,NULL,'<p>Mina est une femelle gibbon de l\'esp&egrave;ce <em>H</em><em>ylobates </em><em>A</em><em>gilis albibarbis</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ce des gibbons qui vit dans le sud de la rivi&egrave;re Kapuas et dans l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito &agrave; Born&eacute;o en &nbsp;Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L\'estimation de l\'ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2001.</p>\r\n<p>Nous l&rsquo;avons r&eacute;cup&eacute;r&eacute;e le 08 octobre 2002 &agrave; Palangkaraya.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;examen medical : Mina est atteinte par la maladie hepatite.</p>\r\n<p>Notes:</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>F&eacute;vrier 2018</p>\r\n<p>Mina va bien. Elle est toujours ensemble avec son compagnon Alex.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2016</p>\r\n<p>Mina et son compagnon Alex vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Comme son compagnon, Mina passe beaucoup de temps en haut de la cage. Mais parfois quand l&rsquo;on passe pr&egrave;s de la cage, Mina aime sauter au grillage pour nous intimider. Elle est agressive avec humain.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2015</p>\r\n<p>Mina et son compagnon Alex vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Mina aime toujours sauter au grillage pour nous intimider quand nous passons pres de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Fevrier 2014</p>\r\n<p>Mina et son compagnon vont bien. Ils sont actifs et mangent bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Septembre 2013</p>\r\n<p>Mina et son compagnon Alex vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Ils sont actifs et mangent bien leur nourriture.</p>\r\n<p>Mina et Alex se balancent souvent en haut de la cage. Mais quand on passe pres de la cage, Mina va sauter au grillage pour nous attraper. Elle n\'aime pas l\'homme.</p>\r\n<p>Le 22 avril 2012</p>\r\n<p>Mina est placee ensemble avec un male gibbon qui s\'appelle Alex. Alex est gentil.</p>\r\n<p>Mina et Alex sont vite devenus amis. Ils chantent ensemble et s\'accouplent.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Janvier 2011</p>\r\n<p>Mina va bien sur notre nouveau site a Pararawen, Muara Teweh. Elle est encore toute seule. <br /><br /> Mars 2010 : Mina est plac&eacute;e pour le moment dans une cage de quarantaine. Mina va &ecirc;tre transf&eacute;r&eacute;e vers notre nouveau site &agrave; Muara Teweh en avril 2010. <br /><br /> Le 11 f&eacute;vrier 2010 : un jour triste pour Mina, son compagnon Mickael est d&eacute;c&eacute;d&eacute;... <br /><br /> Juin 2008 : Mina et son compagnon Mickael s\'entendent bien. Ils continuent &agrave; jouer beaucoup ensemble. <br /><br /> D&eacute;but mai 2008 : Mina et Mickael ont commenc&eacute; d\'avoir des contacts. Ils ont jou&eacute; ensemble. <br /><br /> Le 21 avril 2008 : vers 11 h 14...Mina est plac&eacute;e en m&ecirc;me temps avec un m&acirc;le qui s\'appelle Mickael dans une autre grande voli&egrave;re. Forte heureusement, Mina et Mickael n\'ont pas montr&eacute; des comportements agressifs... <br /><br /> le 14 novembre 2005 : Gugun est d&eacute;c&eacute;d&eacute;... <br /><br /> Novembre 2004 : Une autre jeune femelle gibbon est plac&eacute;e avec Mina, Gredi et Gugun... <br /><br /> Juin 2003 : une autre jeune femelle gibbon qui s\'appelle Gredi est plac&eacute;e avec Mina et Gugun... <br /><br /> 2003 : Mina est transport&eacute;e dans notre refuge qui se trouve sur une &icirc;le ( l\'&icirc;le Hampapak ). Avant Mina a eu d&eacute;ja un compagnon nomm&eacute; Pecki, mais nous avons d&ucirc; la s&eacute;parer de ce compagnon en raison de sa maladie. Mina est ensuite plac&eacute;e dans une grande voli&egrave;re avec un autre jeune gibbon qui s\'appelle Gugun. <br /><br /> Octobre 2002 : Mina est plac&eacute;e dans une cage de quarantaine au Care Center, Palangkaraya.</p>','FR'),
	(51549,75,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:18',NULL,NULL,'<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8683974317292701\">Mina is a female gibbon of the species <em>Hylobates Agilis albibarbis</em>, one of the species of gibbons in the world that lives on Borneo island, Indonesia.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5332763188207931\">Estimation of her birth ye<em>ar&nbsp;</em>: 2001.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6064193162674293\">We rescued her on October 8, 2002 at Palangkaraya.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4268489413006257\">The results of her blood analysis shows that Mina is affected by hepatitis B, tuberculosis and dengue.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.841384251893228\">Notes :</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6585022937699082\">Pararawen centre, Muara Teweh, central Kalimantan, Indonesia.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div>February 2018</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.2567771259892302\">Mina\'s fine. She\'s still together with her companion Alex.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5693644223499844\">Mina is active and eats the fruit well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5454759946085466\">January 2016</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.38841453098418055\">Mina and Alex are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6641631494541723\">As </span><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6641631494541723\">his companion, Mina spends a lot of time at the top of the cage. But sometimes when you pass by the cage, Mina likes to jump to the fence to intimidate us. She\'s aggressive with humans.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7967086689489012\">January 2015</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.985107782822827\">Mina and her mate Alex are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.15849335141455045\">Mina always likes to jump to the fence to intimidate us when we move near the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8578137083050243\">February 2014</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.07737820874864043\">Mina and her companion are fine. They are active and eat the fruit well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8509349036478765\">September 2013</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7585970651392929\">Mina and her mate Alex are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.10804348992611401\">They are active and eat their food well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.05018865562454822\">Mina and Alex often dangle at the top of the cage. But when we pass by the cage, Mina will jump to the fence to catch us. She does not like man.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6807860412664913\">April 22, 2012</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.43059320874058815\">Mina is placed together with a male gibbon called Alex. Alex is nice.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8814380189696424\">Mina and Alex soon became friends. They sing together and mate.</span></div>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3880641856808468\">January 2011</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9207190857729901\">Mina goes well on our new site has Pararawen, Muara Teweh. She\'s still on her own.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.2692421908673658\">March 2010: Mina is placed for the moment in a quarantine cage. Mina is going to be transferred to our new site at Muara Teweh in April 2010.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7102569303334823\">On 11 February 2010: A sad day for Mina, her companion Mickael died ...</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.17800480200261226\">June 2008: Mina and her companion Mickael get along well. They continue to play a lot together.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7841809564449745\">Early May 2008: Mina and Mickael began to have contacts. They played together.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7888624196620668\">April 21, 2008: Around 11:14 am ... Mina is placed at the same time with a male who is called Mickael in another large aviary. Fortunately, Mina and Mickael have not shown aggressive behaviour ...</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7195459048204405\">On 14 November 2005: Gugun died ...</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6280502253736248\">November 2004: Another young female gibbon is placed with Mina, Gredi and Gugun.<br /></span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4136688516355259\">June 2003: Another young female gibbon called Gredi is placed with Mina and Gugun.<br /></span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.1707337842747072\">2003: Mina is transported to our centre which is on (Hampapak Island. Before Mina had already a companion named Pecki, but we had to separate her from this companion because of her illness. Mina is then placed in a large aviary with another young gibbon called Gugun.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.12320898888693177\">October 2002: Mina is placed in a quarantine cage at the Care Center, Palangkaraya.</span></div>\r\n</div>','EN'),
