	(51966,199,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Ningsih est une femelle, n&eacute;e en 1997. Elle appartient &agrave; l\'esp&egrave;ce Syamphalangus Syndactylus (siamang).<br /> Ningsih a &eacute;t&eacute; recueillie par l\'association Kalaweit le 2 d&eacute;cembre 2004 &agrave; Jakarta.<br /> Celle-ci &eacute;tait alors tr&egrave;s traumatis&eacute;e.<br /><br /> Actuellement Ningsih est en tr&egrave;s bonne sant&eacute; et se trouve sur l\'&icirc;le Marak, pr&egrave;s de Padang &agrave; l\'ouest de Sumatra.</p>','FR'),
	(51967,199,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Ningsih is a female, born in 1997. She belongs to the species of Symphalangus syndactylus (siamang).Ningsih was found by Kalaweit on December 2nd 2004 in Jakarta. He was in a very bad condition and suffering from shock. Now Ningsih is in good health and is on Marak island, near Padang on the west coast of Sumatera.</p>','EN'),
