	(51982,203,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'Rarra est une femelle née en 1993, elle appartient &agrave;  l\'espèce Syamphalangus Syndactylus (siamang).<br> \nRarra a été saisie &agrave;  Jakarta avec un mâle, Kato.<br> Nous pensons qu\'elle est apte &agrave;  retourner très prochainement dans la nature.<br><br>Rarra est en bonne santé et séjourne actuellement dans une grande cage sur l\'île Marak &agrave;  l\'ouest de Sumatra. \n','FR'),
	(51983,203,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'Rarra is a female born in 1993 and she belongs to the species of Symphalangus syndactylus (siamang). Rarra was found in Jakarta with a male called Kato.\r\nWe think she is ready to be released back to her forest home in the very near future.\r\nRarra is healthy in a large cage on Marak island in the west of Sumatra. After she is released the KALAWEIT	 team will continue to look after Rarra from a distance, checking that she is healthy and happy in the forest. Even once she is released she will need support from KALAWEIT and she will need a guardian. \r\n','EN'),
