	(52190,643,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Owabie est une femelle gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates agilis ungko</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&icirc;le de Sumatera en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2010.</p>\r\n<p>Owabie a &eacute;t&eacute; confisqu&eacute;e par le department forestier de Jambi ( KSDA ). Ils nous ont confi&eacute; Owabie le 15 f&eacute;vrier 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Ao&ucirc;t 2018</p>\r\n<p>Owabie va bien. Elle est active et mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(52191,643,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Owabie is a female gibbon of <em>Hylobates agilis ungko</em>, one of gibbons species who live in Sumatera, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of her birth year : 2010.</p>\r\n<p>Owabie was confiscated by the department foresty of Jambi. They entrust Owabie to Kalaweit in February, 2 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Center and Santuary, Solok, West Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>August 2018</p>\r\n<p>Owabie is fine. She is active and eat well the fruits.</p>','EN'),
