	(52194,644,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Peter est un m&acirc;le gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates agilis ungko</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;&icirc;le de Sumatera en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2008.</p>\r\n<p>Peter a &eacute;t&eacute; confisqu&eacute; par le department forestier de Jambi. Ils nous ont confi&eacute; Peter le 15 f&eacute;vrier 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Ao&ucirc;t 2018</p>\r\n<p>Peter va bien. Il est actif et mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(52195,644,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Peter is a male gibbon of<em> Hylobates agilis ungko</em>, one of gibbons species who live in Sumatera, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of his birth year : 2008.</p>\r\n<p>Peter was confiscated by the department foresty of Jambi. They entrusts Peter in February, 15 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Center and Santuary, Muara Teweh, Central Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>August 2018</p>\r\n<p>Peter is fine. He is active and eat well the fruits.</p>','EN'),
