	(52241,282,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Dona est une femelle gibbon de l\'esp&egrave;ce <em>H</em><em>ylobates </em><em>M</em><em>uelleri muelleri</em>, l\'une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit dans le sud est Born&eacute;o en Indonesie, approximativement au sud la rivi&egrave;re de Mahakam et &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re de Barito.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>L\'estimation de sa naissance : 1998.</p>\r\n<p>Dona est entr&eacute;e dans le Programme Kalaweit le 14 avril 2006.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;examen medical : Dona est saine.</p>\r\n<p>Notes &nbsp;:</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Ao&ucirc;t 2018</p>\r\n<p>Dona va bien. Elle est active et mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Le 18 mars 2010</p>\r\n<p>Dona et son compagnon Bidut sont transfer&eacute;s au centre de Pararawen &agrave; Muara Teweh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Ils vont bien.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2008</p>\r\n<p>Dona se trouve dans une grande voli&egrave;re avec un m&acirc;le d&rsquo;une m&ecirc;me esp&egrave;ce qui s&rsquo;appelle Bidut.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Au d&eacute;but, Dona et Bidut ne se sont pas bien entendus. Dona et Bidut se sont souvent mis &agrave; l&rsquo;&eacute;cart l&rsquo;un et l&rsquo;autre.</p>\r\n<p>Aujourd&rsquo;hui Dona et Bidut s\'amusent beaucoup ensemble.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(52242,282,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Dona is a female gibbon of species &nbsp;<em>Hylobates muelleri muelleri ,&nbsp;</em>one of gibbons species who lives in southeast Kalimantan, Indonesia, approximately south of the Mahakam river and west of the Barito river.</p>\r\n<p>Year of birth (estimtion) : 1998.</p>\r\n<p>Dona arrived at Kalaweit arril 14th 2006.</p>\r\n<p>Medicale review : Dona is clean.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and &nbsp;Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan Centrale.</p>\r\n<p>August 2018</p>\r\n<p>Dona and her partner are doing well. They are active and eats the fruits well.</p>\r\n<p>January, 2015</p>\r\n<p>Dona and her partner are doing well. They are active.</p>\r\n<p>Dona likes to approach humans. She goes down and hangs on when we are close to the cage.</p>\r\n<p>Bidut is often on the top of cage.</p>\r\n<p>September 2013</p>\r\n<p>Dona and her partner Bidut are fine. They are active and eat well their food.</p>\r\n<p>Dona and Bidut like to play together on the top of cage.</p>\r\n<p>March, 18 2010</p>\r\n<p>Dona and Bidut have been transfered to our new sanctuaire in Pararawen, Muara Teweh, Centre Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>They are fine.</p>\r\n<p>2008</p>\r\n<p>Dona is now with a male gibbon named Bidut.</p>\r\n<p>They are nice with each other and become friends.</p>','EN'),
