	(52393,328,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Alex est un m&acirc;le gibbon &nbsp;de l\'espece&nbsp;<em>Hylobates Agilis albirbarbis,&nbsp;</em>l\'une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit dans le sud de la rivi&egrave;re Kapuas et dans l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito &agrave; Borneo. en &nbsp;Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>L\'estimatimation de son ann&eacute;e de naissance : 1997</p>\r\n<p>Alex a &eacute;t&eacute; confisqu&eacute; &agrave; Jakarta, la capitale de l\'Indon&eacute;sie. Il est arriv&eacute; &agrave; Kalaweit le 09 ao&ucirc;t 2007.</p>\r\n<p>Les r&eacute;sultats du test sanguin nous a montr&eacute; : Alex est infect&eacute; par hepatite B et tuberculose<br /> Alex est tr&egrave;s calme.Quand on est pr&egrave;s de la cage, Alex aime se pendre &agrave; la paroi pour nous regarder.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>F&eacute;vrier 2018</p>\r\n<p>Alex va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec sa compagne Mina.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2016</p>\r\n<p>Alex et sa compagne Mina vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Alex et Mina passent beaucoup de temps en haut de la cage. Alex aime suspendre au grillage pour regarder les alentours.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2015</p>\r\n<p>Alex et sa compagne Mina vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Alex se voit beaucoup en haut de la cage. Il aime suspendre au grillage pour regarder les alentours.</p>\r\n<p>Alex chante aussi avec sa compagne.</p>\r\n<p>Fevrier 2014</p>\r\n<p>Alex et sa compagne Mina vont bien. Ils sont actifs et mangent bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Alex aime se pendre dans un coin en haut de la cage pour regarder les alentours.</p>\r\n<p>Septembre 2013</p>\r\n<p>Alex et sa compagne Mina vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Ils sont actifs et mangent bien leur nourriture.</p>\r\n<p>Alex se voit souvent en haut de la cage. Mina est agressive. Elle aime sauter au grillage pour nous attraper quand nous passons pres de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Le 22 avril 2012</p>\r\n<p>Alex est plac&eacute; avec une femelle gibbon qui s\'appelle Mina. Mina est gentille.</p>\r\n<p>Alex et Mina sont vite devenus amis. Ils chantent ensemble et s\'accouplent.</p>\r\n<p>Le 16 mars 2010&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Alex est transf&eacute;r&eacute; vers notre nouveau centre qui se trouve &agrave; Muara Teweh, Borneo centre. Alex va bien. </p>\r\n<p>Le 30 septembre 2009&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>un jour triste pour Alex... sa compagne Nure l\'a quitt&eacute;. Nure est d&eacute;c&eacute;d&eacute;e a cause d\'une maladie. <br /><br /> Juillet 2009&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Alex et Nure s\'accouplent souvent. <br /><br /> Le 15 mars 2009&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Alex est plac&eacute; avec une femelle de m&ecirc;me esp&egrave;ce qui s\'appelle Nure. Comme Alex, Nure a &eacute;t&eacute; avant avec un autre gibbon et elle a eu un fils. Mais malheureusement son compagnon et son fils sont d&eacute;c&eacute;d&eacute;s. Alex et Nure n\'ont pas montr&eacute; des comportements agressifs. Ils s\'entendent bien. <br /><br /> Le 06 juillet 2008</p>\r\n<p>Liony est s&eacute;par&eacute;e d\'Alex. Ils se sont battus. Liony a une blessure sur son bras gauche. Alex a une petite blessure sur son l&egrave;vre. <br /><br /> Le 01 juillet 2008&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Dans le matin, Liony et Alex sont plac&eacute;s dans une nouvelle voli&egrave;re. Liony a beaucoup approch&eacute; Alex. Mais Alex l\'a ignor&eacute;e. Il se d&eacute;place quand Liony l\'approche. Liony etait un peu agressive au moment de manger. Elle a intimid&eacute; Alex quand Alex voulait entrer dans le couloir pour prendre la nourriture. <br /><br /></p>','FR'),
	(52394,328,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Alex is a male gibbon of the species of <em>Hylobates agilis albirbarbis</em>, one of&nbsp; gibbons species who lives on the island of Borneo in Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimatimation of his birth: 1997.</p>\r\n<p>Alex was confiscated in Jakarta, the capital of Indonesia. He arrived at Kalaweit the 9th of Aug 2007.</p>\r\n<p>The results of the blood test showed us that Alex is infected with hepatitis B and tuberculosis.</p>\r\n<p>Alex is very quiet. When we\'re near the cage, Alex likes to hang himself on the wall to look at us.</p>\r\n<p>Notes:</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Central Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>February 2018</p>\r\n<p>Alex is fine. He is always with his partner Mina.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.12213772733816675\">In the morning, Alex and Mina also sing with the other gibbons.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.48221813887453036\">After singing, Alex likes to move and hang himself at the top of the cage. Sometimes he goes down a bit to look for insects or leaves.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.2539020755186001\">Alex eats the fruit well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.09029274456695424\">January 2016</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.1504749574899683\">Alex and his partner Mina are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4207899860091291\">Alex and Mina spend a lot of time at the top of the cage. Alex likes to hang out at the fence to look around.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.02300072749368931\">January 2015</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.977370162142255\">Alex and his partner Mina are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5796328399220075\">Alex sees a lot at the top of the cage. He likes to hang out at the fence to look around.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.15981952750521267\">Alex also sings with his partner.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.758191681264709\">February 2014</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5136584031787325\">Alex and his partner Mina are fine. They are active and eat the fruit well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.19843129604099463\">Alex likes to hang himself in a corner at the top of the cage to look around.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8478203247946912\">September 2013</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3858497870808626\">Alex and his partner Mina are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5560923082518322\">They are active and eat their food well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6614270271446984\">Alex often sees himself at the top of the cage. Mina is aggressive. She likes to jump to the fence to catch us when we pass by the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.027473750807442632\">April 22, 2012</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6079706059956389\">Alex is now with a female gibbon called Mina. Mina is nice.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.011559857455517686\">Alex and Mina soon became friends. They sing together and mate.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5162507266184194\">March 16, 2010</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8930940473071943\">Alex is transferred to our new center located in Muara Teweh, Borneo Centre. Alex is fine.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8230056549930447\">September 30, 2009</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5724842031425459\">A sad day for Alex ... his companion Nure left him. Nure died because of a disease.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.12937318264424225\">July 2009</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6004977625818393\">Alex and Nure often mate.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3124320689355957\">March 15, 2009</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.04556697446248914\">Alex is placed with a female of the same species called Nure. Like Alex, Nure was before with another gibbon that has had a son. But unfortunately her companion and son are deceased. Alex and Nure have not shown aggressive behaviour. They get along well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.2564232279319113\">July 06, 2008</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.22711061293949486\">Liony is separated from Alex. They were fighting. Liony has a wound on his left arm. Alex has a little wound on his lip.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.1994407328974822\">July 01, 2008</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5324929067600864\">In the morning, Liony and Alex are placed in a new aviary. Liony approached Alex a lot. But Alex ignored her. He moves when Liony approaches him. Liony was a little aggressive when he ate. She intimidated Alex when Alex wanted to enter the hallway to take the food.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n</div>','EN'),
