	(52446,344,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Amang est un m&acirc;le gibbon ( <em>Hylobates agilis ungko </em>)de l\'ile Sumatera, Indonesie. <br /><br /> L\'estimation de l\'annee de sa naissance : 2003. <br /><br /> Amang a ete recupere a Sumatera le 09 janvier 2003. <br /><br /> Amang a la fourrure &eacute;paisse et noire, bien fournie dans la lumi&egrave;re du soleil. Amang est tr&egrave;s acrobatique et il chante fort aussi. <br /><br /> son carnet :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Sanctuaire, Solok, a l\'ouest de Sumatera, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2018</p>\r\n<p>Amang va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Il est actif &agrave; se balancer et &agrave; chanter avec les autres gibbons et siamangs.</p>\r\n<p>Comme d&rsquo;habitude, dans le matin, Amang passe aussi de temps &agrave; chercher des insectes.</p>\r\n<p>Amang mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Quand l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe vient pour donner les fruits, Amang s&rsquo;asseoit sur une branche &eacute;tendue. Il regarde l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe et les alentours de la cage. Amang regarde les alentours parcequ&rsquo;il y a un gibbon sauvage qui aime venir pour prendre aussi les fruits sur le mangeoir d&rsquo;Amang.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2014</p>\r\n<p>Amang va bien. Il est actif a se balancer.</p>\r\n<p>Apr&egrave;s avoir balance, Amang aime s&rsquo;asseoir et s&rsquo;allonger sur une branche etendue. La, il passe de temps a s&rsquo;epouiller.</p>\r\n<p>Amang mange bien les fruits et la nourriture suplementaire comme poulet, oeuf dur et lait.</p>\r\n<p>Amang aime manger les bananes en premier.</p>\r\n<p>Septembre 2013</p>\r\n<p>Amang va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Il est actif a se balancer.</p>\r\n<p>Amang mange aussi bien sa nourriture. Il prend et mange en premier les bananes. Apres il prend et mange d&rsquo;autres fruits comme papaye, pasteque, ananas, mandarin, concombre, carotte et haricot.</p>\r\n<p>Amang aime manger sur une branche etendue en haut de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2013</p>\r\n<p>Amang est maintenant a notre nouveau refuge a Supayang, Solok, a l\'ouest de Padang.</p>\r\n<p>Amang va bien. Il est actif et mange bien ses fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Octobre 2012</p>\r\n<p>Amang va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Amang a ete actif a se balancer et a chanter en haut de la cage. Amang redescend seulement quand il veut prendre la nourriture.</p>\r\n<p>Amang aime aussi apporter et manger ses fruits en haut de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Amang a bien mange sa nourriture.</p>\r\n<p>Fevrier 2012</p>\r\n<p>Amang va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Amang est actif a se balancer et a chanter en haut de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Amang chante aussi fort que d&rsquo;autres gibbons et siamangs. Il aime chanter debout sur une branche.</p>\r\n<p>Juillet 2010</p>\r\n<p>Amang va bien sur l\'ile Marak, Padang, a l\'ouest de Sumatera.</p>','FR'),
	(52447,344,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.0952716314308194\">Amang is a male gibbon (Hylobates agilis Ungko) from the island Sumatera, Indonesia.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9110704940317432\">The estimate of the Year of birth: 2003.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5881909555808559\">Amang was recovered a Sumatera on 09 January 2003.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8914796480350429\">Amang has thick and black fur, well supplied in sunlight. Amang is very acrobatic and he sings hard too.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div>Notes :</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Supayang Conservation Centre and Sanctuary, Solok, west of Sumatera.</div>\r\n<div class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">January 2018</div>\r\n<div class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">Amang is fine.</div>\r\n<div class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6670067631587542\">He is active in swinging, singing and looking for insects in the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.20432206988444257\">Amang eats fruit as well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7679916299049754\">When the team comes to give the fruit, Amang will sits and look at the team on an extended branch at the top of the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3610045416137825\">Amang comes down and approaches the manger when the team moves away from the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.12127363695924187\">But in order to take and eat the fruit on the feeder Amang looks at the surroundings first. He has this habit since the presence of a wild gibbon who likes to come to take the fruits.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7432822262936075\">January 2014</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8020662118009936\">Amang\'s fine. He\'s active in swinging.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9670924741877157\">After balancing, Amang likes to sit and lie down on an extended branch. There he spends time looking for lice.<br /></span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6529751835120936\">Amang eats well the fruits and food aditional as chicken, hard-boiled egg and milk.</span><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6740337456157263\"> Amang likes to eat bananas first.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3730561270603481\">September 2013</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8594039222227325\">Amang\'s fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.68559555746935\">He\'s active in swinging.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3069670269996402\">Amang eats his food as well. He takes and eats the bananas first. After it takes and eats other fruits like papaya, watermelon, pineapple, mandarin, cucumber, carrot and bean.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8933452262720496\">Amang likes to eat on an extended branch at the top of the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3357365025654495\">April 2013</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.25304945087921404\">Amang is now at our new refuge in Supayang, Solok, west of Padang.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4733428240347405\">Amang\'s fine. It is active and eats well its fruits.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.18817164949684784\">October 2012</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.36094676292914674\">Amang\'s fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9024547447943511\">Amang was active in swinging and singing at the top of the cage. Amang only comes down when he wants to take the food.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.07433521463501724\">Amang also likes to bring and eat his fruit at the top of the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4305523493952417\">Amang ate his food well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7351901426521932\">February 2012</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8049493501349234\">Amang\'s fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.11775861219097905\">Amang is active in swinging and singing at the top of the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9569343284374938\">Amang sings as loud as other gibbons and siamangs. He likes to sing standing on a tree branch.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9154384120934858\">July 2010</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.25040496150369085\">Amang goes well on the island Marak, Padang, west of Sumatera.</span></div>\r\n</div>','EN'),
