	(52597,389,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Ally est une femelle siamang ( <em>Symphalangus syndactylus </em>) de l\'ile Sumatera, Indonesie. <br /><br /> Estimation de l\'ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2000. <br /><br /> Ally a &eacute;t&eacute; confisqu&eacute;e &agrave; Jakarta, Java. Elle est entr&eacute;e dans Kalaweit Programme en 2006. <br /><br /> Ally est saine. <br /><br />notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, a l\'ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2018</p>\r\n<p>Ally va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Elle est active &agrave; se balancer et &agrave; chanter avec les autres siamangs et gibbons.</p>\r\n<p>Comme d&rsquo;habitude dans le matin, Ally aime prendre des bains de soleil et faire sa toilette en haut de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Ally mange aussi bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Ally se balance un peu quand l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe vient pour donner les fruits. Puis elle va attendre les fruits derri&egrave;re le mangeoire.</p>\r\n<p>Ally prend et mange en premier les bananes avant de prendre les autres fruits comme papaye ou pasteque.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2014</p>\r\n<p>Ally va bien. Elle est active a se balancer et&nbsp; a chercher des insectes.</p>\r\n<p>Apr&egrave;s avoir balance et cherche des insectes, Ally aime s&rsquo;asseoir longuement sur une branche etendue.</p>\r\n<p>Ally mange bien les fruits et la nourriture suplementaire comme poulet, oeuf dur et lait.</p>\r\n<p>Septembre 2013</p>\r\n<p>Ally va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Elle est active et aime se se balancer.</p>\r\n<p>Ally mange aussi bien sa nourriture. Elle prend et mange en premier les bananes. Apr&egrave;s elle prend et mange d&rsquo;autres fruits comme papaye, pasteque, ananas, mandarin, concombre, carotte et haricot.</p>\r\n<p>Ally aime manger pr&egrave;s de sa mangeoire.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2013</p>\r\n<p>Ally va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Ally est active a se balancer et a chanter avec d&rsquo;autres siamangs et gibbons.</p>\r\n<p>Ally aime se balancer et se suspendre &agrave; une des cordes qui sont tendues dans la voli&egrave;re.</p>\r\n<p>Ally mange bien ses fruits.</p>\r\n<p>F&eacute;vrier 2012</p>\r\n<p>Ally va bien. Ally est active a se balancer et &agrave; chanter avec d\'autres siamangs et gibbons.</p>\r\n<p>Ally mange bien ses fruits.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Le 23 juin 2011</p>\r\n<p>Un jour triste pour Ally, son compagnon Alan est d&eacute;ced&eacute;. Alan est tomb&eacute; malade pendant une semaine. Il a eu la diarh&eacute;e et n\'a pas surv&eacute;cu. <br /><br /> Fevrier 2011<br /> Alan et Ally vont bien. <br /><br /> Ils sont actifs. <br /><br /> Alan aime chercher des insectes et prendre des feuilles en bas de la cage. <br /><br /> Ally aime s\'asseoir en haut de la cage. Elle regarde parfois Alan. <br /><br /> Alan et Ally se disputent un peu pendant la nourrisage. C\'est toujours Ally qui est dominante. <br /><br /> Alan va prendre sa nouriture quand Ally s\'eloigne de la mangeoire. <br /><br /> Le 11 f&eacute;vrier 2010<br /><br /> un jour triste pour Alen et Ally... leur fils Henry est d&eacute;c&eacute;d&eacute;. Henry a &eacute;t&eacute; malade. Il a eu la diarrh&eacute;e. <br /><br /> Janvier 2010<br /> Ally et sa famille vont bien. Ils sont toujours ensemble sur l\'ile Marak, Padang - Sumatera. <br /><br /> Ally a donn&eacute; naissance &agrave; un b&eacute;b&eacute; . Et nous appellons son b&eacute;b&eacute; Henry. <br /><br /> 2006<br /> Ally est plac&eacute;e avec un m&acirc;le qui s\'appelle Alan. Tous les deux s\'entendent bien.</p>','FR'),
	(52598,389,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9815886481602217\">Ally is a female Siamang (Symphalangus syndactylus) from Ile Sumatera, Indonesia.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9570830092444219\">Estimate of the year of birth: 2000.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.26290398232044987\">Ally was confiscated in Jakarta, Java. She entered Kalaweit program in 2006.</span><span id=\"noHighlight_0.21077146396990187\"> Ally\'s healthy.</span></div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.2568126437442819\">Notes :</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3729562800050443\">Supayang Conservation Centre and Sanctuary, Solok, west of Sumatera.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6029045003198124\">January 2018</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span>Ally is fine. She is active.</span></div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span>In the morning, Ally like also to take sunbath at the top of cage.</span></div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span>Ally eat well the fruits. She always like to eat&nbsp; first bananas before eating others fruits like papaya or water melon.</span></div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6248060073390599\">January 2014</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5001403269922455\">Ally\'s fine. She\'s active in swinging and looking for bugs.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4804404185138662\">After balancing and looking for insects, Ally likes to sit at length on an extended branch.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9535564515103626\">Ally eats well the fruits and food aditional as chicken, hard-boiled egg and milk.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.37799221515761405\">September 2013</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.321658524242472\">Ally\'s fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9332011374722461\">She\'s active and likes to swing.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.34516886880606923\">Ally eats her food as well. She takes and eats the bananas first. After it takes and eats other fruits like papaya, watermelon, pineapple, mandarin, cucumber, carrot and bean.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5947255863890524\">Ally likes to eat near her manger.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3302025793339245\">April 2013</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9375521124368501\">Ally\'s fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9422234993247139\">Ally is active in swinging and singing with other siamangs and Gibbons.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5981450882329801\">Ally likes to swing and hang on to one of the ropes that are stretched in the aviary.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.31401225017854706\">Ally eats his fruit well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.09698798866505176\">February 2012</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.485374119644316\">Ally\'s fine. Ally is active in swinging and singing with other siamangs and Gibbons.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.13332099165072642\">Ally eats his fruit well.</span></div>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.834982384148562\">June 23, 2011</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.2072173501116903\">One sad day for Ally, her companion Alan is dies. Alan fell ill for a week. He had the diarrhea and did not survive.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7759042609990159\">February 2011</span></div>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.41546531733758263\">Alan and Ally are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7802680628009903\">They\'re active.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5341400829769366\">Alan likes to look for insects and take leaves down the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8372527954623034\">Ally likes to sit at the top of the cage. She sometimes looks at Alan.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4364820430871611\">Alan and Ally are arguing a little bit during the nourrisage. It\'s always Ally who\'s dominant.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.1442275613806926\">Alan will take his food when Ally gets away from the manger.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.13197920692677612\">February 11, 2010</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5460107317053354\">A sad day for Alen and Ally ... their son Henry died. Henry was sick. He had diarrhea.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6199354148606512\">January 2010</span></div>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6546720885656389\">Ally and her family are fine. They are still together on the island Marak, Padang-Sumatera.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9166484532118888\">Ally gave birth to a baby. And we call her baby Henry.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8468368806735698\">2006</span></div>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.07019801494955336\">Ally is placed with a male named Alan. Both of them get along well.</span></div>\r\n</div>','EN'),
