	(52607,393,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p><span>Zacky Dewasa est un m&acirc;le siamang (&nbsp;<em><span>Symphalangus syndactylus&nbsp;</span></em>)de Sumatera, Indon&eacute;sie.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> L\'estimation de l\'ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2000.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Zacky Dewasa a &eacute;t&eacute; confisqu&eacute; par BKSDA &agrave; Jakarta.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Zacky dewasa est entr&eacute; dans Kalaweit Programme en 2008.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Zacky Dewasa est atteint par Herpes Simplex.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Notes :</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Supayang&nbsp; Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, a l\'ouest de Sumatera.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Mai 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec sa famille.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>F&eacute;vrier 2016</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Observation par : Andre.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky&nbsp; Dewasa, Angkung et leur fils Angel et Ozy Kecil &nbsp;vont bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ce mois l&rsquo;observation se passe en regardant les r&eacute;actions de siamangs et gibbons quand il y a humain pr&egrave;s de la cage.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Quand il y a humain pr&egrave;s de la cage, Zacky Dewasa, Angkung et Angel se balancent beaucoup. Ils sautent et frappent aussi le grillage avec leurs pattes. Apr&egrave;s avoir balanc&eacute;, Zacky Dewasa et Angkung nous approchent et nous regardent comme ils attendaient les fruits. Angel reste en haut de la cage. Comme sa m&egrave;re, Angel nous attaque quand nous sommes n&eacute;gligents.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ozy Kecil va s&rsquo;attacher &agrave; sa maman.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung et Angel mangent bien les fruits.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Decembre 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Le 03 decembre 2015 Angkung a donn&eacute; naissance &agrave; un b&eacute;b&eacute; siamang. C\'est un m&acirc;le. Nous appellons le b&eacute;b&eacute; Ozy.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angkung et son bebe vont bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Janvier 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung et leur fils Angel vont bien. Ils sont actifs &agrave; se balancer, &agrave; chanter et &agrave; jouer ensemble.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Janvier 2014</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et sa famille vont bien. Ils sont actifs &agrave; se balancer et &agrave; jouer.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa aime s&rsquo;approcher de sa compagne pour jouer. Il attrape et tire Angkung. Puis il court quand Angkung veut l&rsquo;attraper.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et Angkung jouent aussi en se mordant.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angel s&rsquo;attache encore souvent &agrave; sa maman. Parfois elle se d&eacute;tache un peu et apprend &agrave; se balancer &agrave; une branche. Mais elle reste pr&egrave;s de sa maman.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et Angkung mangent bien les fruits et la nourriture suplementaire comme poulet, oeuf dur et lait.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Septembre 2013</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung et Angel vont bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ils sont actifs et mangent bien leur nourriture.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et Angkung prennent et mangent en premier les bananes. Apr&egrave;s ils reprennent et mangent d&rsquo;autres fruits comme papaye, pasteque, ananas, mandarin, concombre, carotte et haricot.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et Angkung aiment manger pr&egrave;s du couloir.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angel t&eacute;te souvent &agrave; sa maman.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Juin 2013</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Le 26 juin 2013, Angkung a donn&eacute; naissance &agrave; un b&eacute;b&eacute; siamang. Angkung et son b&eacute;b&eacute; sont sains et saufs.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Nous appellons le b&eacute;b&eacute; Angel.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Octobre 2012</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et sa compagne Angkung vont bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et Angkung sont actifs &agrave; se balancer sur les branches et les cordes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angkung aime aussi redescendre au sol. Elle aime creuser la terre avec ses mains.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et Angkung ont bien mang&eacute; leur nourriture.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Juin 2012</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ce mois, Zacky Dewasa et Angkung se sont remis ensemble.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Janvier 2012</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa est tout seul dans la cage.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angkung est plac&eacute;e dans une autre cage. Elle a d&ucirc; &ecirc;tre separ&eacute;e de Napoleon en raison des ses comportements.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angkung a abandonn&eacute; Napoleon.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Napoleon est soign&eacute; &agrave; la clinique.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Le 11 decembre 2011 Angkung a donn&eacute; naissance &agrave; un b&eacute;b&eacute; siamang. Vers 07 h 30, Angkung etait faible. Elle s\'allongeait beaucoup.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Puis vers 10 h 30, Angkung a commenc&eacute; de s\'agiter comme elle voulait donner naissance.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> De 13 h 30 a 14 h 15, intervention medicale pour l\'aider.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> 19 h 00, l\'equipe veterinaire a d&ucirc; anesthesier Angkung pour l\'aider.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> L\'equipe veterinaire a d&ucirc; tirer le b&eacute;b&eacute; et pousser le ventre d\'Angkung pour faire sortir le b&eacute;b&eacute;.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Vers 21 h 30, le b&eacute;b&eacute; a pu sortir. Il est sain et sauf. La mere est sauve aussi.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Comme Angkung etait faible et n\'a pas pu s\'occuper de son bebe, nous avons amen&eacute; son b&eacute;b&eacute; &agrave; la Clinique pour des soins.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Nous appellons le bebe d\'Angkung et Zacky Dewasa Napoleon.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span><br /> Fevrier 2011&nbsp;<br /> <!--[endif]--></span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa est maintenant avec une femelle siamang qui s\'appelle Angkung. Ils s\'entendent bien.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Ils ont bien mang&eacute; leurs fruits ce matin - la.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Apr&egrave;s avoir mang&eacute; Zacky Dewasa et Angkung se sont remis &agrave; jouer ensemble.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Zacky Dewasa et Angkung se sont aussi accoupl&eacute;s en haut de la cage.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Apr&egrave;s avoir jou&eacute;, Zacky Dewasa s\'est mis &agrave; epouiller sa compagne.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br /> <!--[endif]--></span></p>','FR'),
	(52608,393,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa is a male Siamang (<em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em>) from Sumatera, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>The estimation of his birth year : 2000.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa was confiscated by BKSDA in Jakarta.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa entered Kalaweit program in 2008.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa is infected by herpes Simplex.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre and Sanctuary, Solok, west of Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>May 2018</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and his family are all fine. They are active and eat the fruit well.</p>\r\n<p>February 2016</p>\r\n<p>Observation by: Andre.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung and their son Angel and Ozzie Kecil are fine.</p>\r\n<p>This month the observation happens by looking at the reactions of siamangs and Gibbons when there is human near the cage.</p>\r\n<p>When there is human near the cage, Zacky Dewasa, Angkung and Angel sway a lot. They jump and also hit the fence with their paws. After swinging, zacky Dewasa and Angkung approach us and look at us as they waited for the fruit. Angel stays at the top of the cage. Like his mother, Angel attacks us when we\'re careless.</p>\r\n<p>Ozzie Kecil will attach himself to his mother.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung and Angel eat the fruit well.</p>\r\n<p>December 2015</p>\r\n<p>On December 03, 2015 Angkung gave birth to a Bebe Siamang. He\'s a male. We call the Bebe Ozzie.</p>\r\n<p>Angkung and her baby are fine.</p>\r\n<p>January 2015</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung and their son Angel are fine. They are active in swinging, singing and playing together.</p>\r\n<p>January 2014</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and his family are fine. They are active in swinging and playing.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa likes to get close to his partner to play. He catches and shoots Angkung. Then he runs when Angkung wants to catch him.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and Angkung also play by biting.</p>\r\n<p>Angel still often clings to his mom. Sometimes it comes off a bit and learns to swing to an extended branch. But she stays close to her mom.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and Angkung eat well the fruits and food aditional as chicken, hard-boiled egg and milk.</p>\r\n<p>September 2013</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung and Angel are fine.</p>\r\n<p>They are active and eat their food well.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and Angkung take and eat bananas first. After they pick up and eat other fruits like papaya, watermelon, pineapple, mandarin, cucumber, carrot and bean.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and Angkung like to eat near the hallway.</p>\r\n<p>Angel suckle often to his mommy.</p>\r\n<p>June 2013</p>\r\n<p>On 26 June 2013, Angkung gave birth to a Bebe Siamang. Angkung and her baby are safe.</p>\r\n<p>We call Bebe Angel.</p>\r\n<p>April 2013</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and his companion Angkung are fine.</p>\r\n<p>They are active in swinging on the branches.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and Angkung eat their fruits well.</p>\r\n<p>October 2012</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and his companion Angkung well.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and Angkung are active in swinging on the branches and ropes.</p>\r\n<p>Angkung also likes to go down to the ground. She loves digging the earth with her hands.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and Angkung have eaten their food well.</p>\r\n<p>July 2012</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa is fine. He\'s still in a quarantine cage for care. He just went through an operation.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa is active in swinging and singing with other siamangs and Gibbons.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa ate his food well.</p>\r\n<p>This month, the veterinary team also gave him treatment against pests.</p>\r\n<p>June 2012</p>\r\n<p>This month, Zacky Dewasa and Angkung got back together.</p>\r\n<p>January 2012</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa is alone in the cage.</p>\r\n<p>Angkung is placed in another cage. She had to be separated from her baby Napoleon because of her behavior.</p>\r\n<p>Angkung has abandoned Napoleon., he is at the veterinary clinic.</p>\r\n<p>On December 11, 2011 Angkung gave birth to a Bebe Siamang. Around 07:30, Angkung was weak. She was very much lying down.</p>\r\n<p>Then around 10:30, Angkung began to agitate as she wanted to give birth.</p>\r\n<p>From 1:30 p.m. to 2:15 p.m., medical intervention to help him.</p>\r\n<p>7:00 p.m., the veterinary team had anesthesier Angkung to assist it.</p>\r\n<p>The veterinary team had to pull the baby and push the belly of Angkung to get the baby out.</p>\r\n<p>Around 9:30, the baby was able to get out. He\'s safe. The mother is safe, too.</p>\r\n<p>As Angkung was weak and could not look after her baby, we brought her Bebe to the clinic for care.</p>\r\n<p>We call the Bebe of Angkung and Zacky Dewasa Napoleon.</p>\r\n<p>February 2011</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa is now with a female siamang who is called Angkung. They get along well.</p>\r\n<p>They ate their fruit well this morning.</p>\r\n<p>After eating zacky Dewasa and Angkung got back to playing together.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa and Angkung also mated at the top of the cage.</p>\r\n<p>After playing, Zacky Dewasa began to search for lice on his companion.<br /> &nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">&nbsp;</div>','EN'),
