	(52737,436,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Kimo est un m&acirc;le siamang ( <em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em> ), l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;&icirc;le Sumatera en Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance&nbsp;: 2001.</p>\r\n<p>Kimo a &eacute;t&eacute; confisqu&eacute; &agrave; Malang, Java centre le 09 ao&ucirc;t 2008.</p>\r\n<p>Le resultat du test sanguin&nbsp;: Kimo est atteint par la maladie H&eacute;patite A.</p>\r\n<p>Notes &nbsp;:</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018</p>\r\n<p>Kimo va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Il est actif &agrave; se balancer et &agrave; chanter avec les autres siamangs et gibbons.</p>\r\n<p>Comme les autres siamangs et gibbons, dans le matin, Kimo aime prendre bains de soleil en haut de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Kimo mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Kimo se montre agressif quand il y a l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe qui donne les fruits. Kimo va sauter partout dans la cage. Il saute et frappe aussi le grillage avec ses deux jambes pour intimider l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe.</p>\r\n<p>Octobre 2010&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Kimo va bien sur l&rsquo;&icirc;le Marak, Padang, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Kimo n&rsquo;a pas encore de compagnon.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(52738,436,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Kimo is a male siamang ( <em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em> ), one of gibbons species who live in Sumatera, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of his birth year : 2001.</p>\r\n<p>Kimo was n in Malang, Java Centrale, on august, 9 2008.</p>\r\n<p>The result of his blood check : Kimo was infected by hepatitis A.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Center and Santuary, Solok, West Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>May&nbsp; 2018</p>\r\n<p>Kimo is fine. He is active. He swing and sing with others siamangs and gibbons.</p>\r\n<p>Like many others siamangs and gibbons, in the morning, Kimo like to take sunbath at the top of cage.</p>\r\n<p>Kimo eat well the fruits. But he is always agressive with the animal keeper who came to give the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Kimo like to jump all around the cage and hit the cage with his foot to intimidate us.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','EN'),
