	(52765,444,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Aladini est une femelle gibbon klossi <em>Hylobates klossi</em>, &nbsp;une esp&egrave;ce de gibbon qui vit uniquement sur l&rsquo;ile Mentawai, Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>Aladini&nbsp; a &eacute;t&eacute; r&eacute;cup&eacute;r&eacute;e le 02 decembre 2010 &agrave; Mentawai.</p>\r\n<p>Le resultat du test sanguin : Aladini est infect&eacute;e par la maladie hepatite.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang &nbsp;Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, a l\'ouest de Sumatera Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2018</p>\r\n<p>Aladini va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Elle est active &agrave; se balancer et &agrave; chanter avec les autres gibbons et siamangs.</p>\r\n<p>Comme d&rsquo;habitude, apr&egrave;s avoir chant&eacute;, Aladini aime chercher des insectes autour de la cage. aladini aime aussi prendre des bains de soleil quand il fait beau dans le matin.</p>\r\n<p>Aladini mange aussi bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Aladini est devenue agressive quand l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe vient pour donner les fruits. Elle saute au grillage pour nous intimider.</p>\r\n<p>Elle se calme quand l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe s&rsquo;&eacute;loigne de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Aladini aime prendre et manger en premier les bananes avant les autres fruits comme papaye ou pasteque.</p>\r\n<p>Juillet 2016</p>\r\n<p>Jack, le compagnon d&rsquo;Aladini s&rsquo;est &eacute;chapp&eacute; de la cage il y a deux semaines.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;&eacute;quipe de Sumatera continue &agrave; chercher Jack jusqu&rsquo;aujourd&rsquo;hui.</p>\r\n<p>Nous esp&egrave;rons&nbsp; que Jack va bien et peut survivre dans la nature qu&rsquo;un jour nous le reverrons.</p>\r\n<p>Fevrier 2016</p>\r\n<p>Aladini et son compagnon Jack vont bien. Ils sont actifs et mangent bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2015</p>\r\n<p>Aladini et son compagnon Jack vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Ils sont actifs a se balancer, a chanter et a jouer ensemble.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2014</p>\r\n<p>Jack et sa compagne Aladini vont bien. Ils sont actifs a se balancer et a jouer.</p>\r\n<p>Aladini aime toujours sauter et frapper son compagnon. Jack pousse des petits cris. Puis il poursuit Aladini.</p>\r\n<p>Jack et Aladini mangent bien les fruits et la nourriture suplementaire comme papaye, oeuf dur et lait.</p>\r\n<p>Septembre 2013</p>\r\n<p>Jack et sa compagne Aladini vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Ils sont actifs a se balancer.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Jack et Aladini mangent aussi bien leur nourriture. Ils prennent et mangent en premier les bananes. Apres ils prennent et mangent d&rsquo;autres fruits comme papaye, pasteque, ananas, mandarin, concombre, carotte et haricot.</p>\r\n<p>Jack aime manger pres du mangeoire. Aladini aime manger sur une branche etendue en haut de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2013</p>\r\n<p>Jack et sa compagne Aladini vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Jack et Aladini sont actif a se balancer et a jouer ensemble.</p>\r\n<p>Ils jouent beaucoup en se poursuivant et en s&rsquo;attrapant.</p>\r\n<p>Jack et Aladini mangent bien leurs fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Octobre 2012</p>\r\n<p>Jack et sa compagne Aladini&nbsp; vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Jack et Aladini sont actifs a se balancer et a jouer.</p>\r\n<p>Jack aime jouer sur le sol. Sa compagne Aladini joue souvent sur les cordes en haut de la cage. Elle saute aussi au sol.</p>\r\n<p>Jack et Aladini ont bien mange leur nourriture.</p>\r\n<p>Mars 2011&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Aladini va bien dans notre site qui se trouve sur l\'ile Marak, a l\'ouest de Padang, Sumatera.</p>','FR'),
	(52766,444,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5287629005946777\">Aladini is a female gibbon of Klossi (<em>Hylobates klossii</em>) of the island Mentawai, Indonesia.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.40647745707182714\">Aladini was rescued on December, 2 2010 in Mentawai.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3886117728587334\">The result of her blood test: Aladini is infected with hepatitis disease.</span></div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">Notes :</div>\r\n<div class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.22680296790563703\">Supayang Conservation Centre and Sanctuary, Solok, west of Sumatera Indonesia.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6167679623926112\">January 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6702608342072611\">Aladini\'s fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5809899007562134\">She is active at moving, singing and looking for insects in the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.1488007889903168\">Aladini spends a lot of time looking for insects. After looking for insects, Aladini likes to rest at the top of the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8469663450073699\">When the time of the fooding comes, Aladini is aggressive. She jumps to the fence to scratch and bite.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8784236593449306\">Aladini eats the fruit well. She like to eat first bananas before eating others fruits like papaya or water melon.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.16336486248817383\">July 2016</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8631612577719252\">Jack, Aladini\'s companion escaped from the cage two weeks ago.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.033588295695706316\">Sumatra\'s team keeps looking for Jack until today.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.827525006303901\">We hope that Jack is well and can survive in nature that one day we will see him again.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.24642570031825928\">February 2016</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.40077178674220915\">Aladini and his companion Jack are fine. They are active and eat the fruit well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7684667444763792\">January 2015</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9198231002256522\">Aladini and his companion Jack are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.43077581479963867\">They are active in swinging, singing and playing together.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7907508148770857\">January 2014</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5317541238122413\">Jack and his girlfriend Aladini are fine. They are active in swinging and playing.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.002300850434598267\">Aladini always likes to jump and hit his companion. Jack pushes little cries. Then he pursues Aladini.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.37431905435536816\">Jack and Aladini eat well the fruits and food aditional as papaya, hard-boiled egg and milk.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4759840571516405\">September 2013</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5984083836125565\">Jack and his girlfriend Aladini are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.823517572890985\">They\'re active in swinging.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.10035745364516158\">Jack and Aladini eat their food as well. They take and eat the bananas first. After they take and eat other fruits like papaya, watermelon, pineapple, mandarin, cucumber, carrot and bean.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.2613604704039981\">Jack likes to eat near the feeder. Aladini likes to eat on an extended branch at the top of the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4676010992490255\">April 2013</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3096011863749484\">Jack and his girlfriend Aladini are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6144406270786277\">Jack and Aladini are active in swinging and playing together.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5087456318645943\">They play a lot by pursuing and catching themselves.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.07102725527184794\">Jack and Aladini eat their fruits well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9511877271715868\">October 2012</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7861673609545093\">Jack and his girlfriend Aladini are fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6944488955164282\">Jack and Aladini are active in swinging and playing.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5498977566747291\">Jack likes to play on the floor. His companion Aladini often plays on the ropes at the top of the cage. She\'s also jumping on the ground.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9196843544198013\">Jack and Aladini ate their food well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.1852098351908288\">March 2011</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.24771626578148798\">Aladini goes well in our site which is located on the island Marak, west of Padang, Sumatera.</span></div>\r\n</div>','EN'),
