	(52850,469,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Aming est un m&acirc;le siamang&nbsp; (<em> Symphalangus syndactylus&nbsp;</em>) qui vit sur l\'&icirc;le de Sumatera, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>L\'estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2008.</p>\r\n<p>Aming a &eacute;t&eacute; r&eacute;cup&eacute;r&eacute;&nbsp;&agrave; Padang le 23 fevrier 2012.</p>\r\n<p>L\'histoire :</p>\r\n<p>Comme d&rsquo;autres animaux sauvages, Aming a subi un traumatisme quand les gens l&rsquo;ont captur&eacute; et amene loin de son univers, la foret et tous ses habitants.</p>\r\n<p>Aming vit alors comme un animal de compagnie avec les gens.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Sanctuaire, Solok,&nbsp;&agrave; l\'ouest de Sumatera, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018</p>\r\n<p>Aming va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec sa compagne Kresna.</p>\r\n<p>Le 27 ao&ucirc;t 2017</p>\r\n<p>Aming et Kresna sont mis ensemble en couple. Ils vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2017</p>\r\n<p>Observation faites par : Andre.</p>\r\n<p>Aming va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Il est actif &agrave; se balancer, &agrave; chanter, &agrave; jouer et &agrave; chercher des insectes dans la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Aming aime jouer avec les cordes &eacute;tendues. Il les mord et les tire. Apr&egrave;s avoir jou&eacute;, Aming se met &agrave; chercher des insectes.</p>\r\n<p>Aming mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Quand l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe vient pour donner les fruits, Aming se deplace partout dans la cage. Puis il s&rsquo;asseoit pr&egrave;s del la mangeoire pour attendre ses fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Aming prend et mange les fruits quand l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe s&rsquo;&eacute;loigne de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2014</p>\r\n<p><span>Aming va bien. Il est actif &agrave; se balancer, &agrave; jouer et &agrave; chanter avec d&rsquo;autres siamangs et gibbons.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming joue avec ses pattes. Il les attrape et les mord.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming n&rsquo;aime pas quand il y a humain pr&egrave;s de la cage. Il va sauter et frapper le grillage avec ses pattes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Amin mange bien les fruits et la nourriture suplementaire comme poulet, oeuf dur et lait.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Septembre 2013</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming va bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming est actif &agrave; se balancer.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming mange bien sa nourriture.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Il prend et mange toujours en premier les bananes. Apr&egrave;s il prend et mange d&rsquo;autres fruits comme papaye, ananas, pasteque, mandarin, concombre, carotte et haricot.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming aime manger pres de la mangeoire.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Avril 2013</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming va bien. Il est actif &agrave; se balancer et &agrave; jouer. Aming aime mordre ses pattes en jouant.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming mange bien ses fruits</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Le septembre 2012</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming est transfer&eacute; vers notre refuge pour les animaux de Sumatera &agrave; Supayang, Solok, &agrave; l\'ouest de Sumatra.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming va bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Fevrier 2012</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Aming va bien. Il est maintenant dans notre refuge qui se trouve sur l&rsquo;ile Marak, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Padang, Sumatera.</span></p>','FR'),
	(52851,469,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.007944556788367474\">Aming is a male Siamang (Symphalangus syndactylus) from Sumatera, Indonesia.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.19582004457647606\">Estimate of the year of birth: 2008.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6139459968615313\">Aming was recovered a Padang on 23 February 2012.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7764690173904613\">His story:</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8786666628452203\">Like other wild animals, Aming suffered a trauma when people captured him and brought him away from his universe, the forest and all its inhabitants ...</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4972268774605282\">His life in freedom ended when people put a chain around his neck.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div>notes :</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.10033349389198198\">Supayang Conservation Center and Santuary, Solok, west of Sumatera, Indonesia.</span></div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span>May 2018</span></div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div>Aming is fine. He is always with his partner Kresna.</div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span>August, 27 2017</span></div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span>Aming and Kresna are now together as a couple. They are just fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.36504979044244\">January 2017</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.44006811943826196\">Observation made by: Andre.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.49476123416965534\">Aming\'s fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.46823680795612155\">He is active in swinging, singing, playing and looking for insects in the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.6440991943375038\">Aming likes to play with extended strings. He bites them and shoots them. After playing, Aming starts looking for insects.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.49050562323878033\">Aming eats the fruit well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.005712451758875248\">When the team comes to give the fruit, Aming moves everywhere in the cage. Then he sits near the manger to wait for his fruit.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8135207542287768\">Aming takes and eats fruit when the team moves away from the cage.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7133707572168382\">January 2014</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.35936430290980803\">Aming\'s fine. He is active in swinging, playing and singing with other siamangs and Gibbons.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.298303089014906\">Aming plays with his paws. He catches them and bites them.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.07771420627549275\">Aming does not like when there is human near the cage. He\'s going to jump and hit the fence with his paws.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.021137662467419327\">Amin eats well the fruits and food aditional as chicken, hard-boiled egg and milk.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9516202017927817\">September 2013</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.41479582103998447\">Aming\'s fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.015950341276969704\">Aming is active in swinging.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.09653358989440097\">Aming eats his food well.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.28289414156600445\">He always takes and eats bananas first. After it takes and eats other fruits like papaya, pineapple, watermelon, mandarin, cucumber, carrot and bean.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.10310443636675526\">Aming likes to eat near the feeder.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.33962322119561594\">April 2013</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4692552645824346\">Aming\'s fine. He\'s active in swinging and playing. Aming likes to bite his paws playing.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5848606896229788\">Aming eats well its fruits</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.13859066915235252\">On September 2012</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.8725697496068502\">Aming is transferred to our shelter for animals of Sumatera in Supayang, Solok, west of Sumatera.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.0005908048025589085\">Aming\'s fine.</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.07669313039750425\">February 2012</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5892491674775798\">Aming\'s fine. It is now in our refuge which is located on the island Marak, west of Padang, Sumatra.</span></div>\r\n</div>','EN'),
