	(52854,470,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Tumo est un m&acirc;le gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates Agilis albibarbis</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;ile Born&eacute;o, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance&nbsp;: 2005.</p>\r\n<p>Tumo a &eacute;t&eacute; recuper&eacute; &agrave; Pangkalan Bun, Borneo Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Tumo est arriv&eacute; &agrave; Kalaweit le 12 janvier 2012.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o.</p>\r\n<p>Le 10 juillet&nbsp; 2018</p>\r\n<p>Un jour triste pour Aphinx, Tumo est d&eacute;ced&eacute;.</p>\r\n<p>Tumo est tomb&eacute; malade. Nous avons d&ucirc; le soigner dans la Clinique. Malheureusement Tumo n&rsquo;a pas survecu.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;&eacute;quipe v&eacute;terinaire a fait de l&rsquo;autopsie, Le r&eacute;sultat nous montre : le foie et le coeur sont d&eacute;grad&eacute;s.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018</p>\r\n<p>Tumo va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec sa compagne Aphinx.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2015</p>\r\n<p>Tumo et sa compagne Aphinx vont bien. Tumo s\'approche aussi de sa compagne pour jouer.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2013</p>\r\n<p>Tumo est maintenant avec une femelle gibbon, Aphinx.</p>\r\n<p>Tumo et Aphinx vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Tumo s\'approche souvent de sa compagne pour jouer.</p>\r\n<p>Mars 2012</p>\r\n<p>Tumo va bien dans notre refuge au camp Pararawen, Muara Teweh, Borneo Centre.</p>','FR'),
	(52855,470,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Tumo is a male gibbon (<em>Hylobates agilis albirbabis</em>) of Borneo, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Year of birth (estimation) : 2005.</p>\r\n<p>Tumo was sauved in Pangkalan Bun, Centre Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>Tumo was arrived at Kalaweit on january, 12 2012.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation&nbsp; Center and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Central Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>July, 10 2018</p>\r\n<p>A sad day for Aphinx, her partner Tumo was died because of illness.</p>\r\n<p>May 2018</p>\r\n<p>Tumo and his partner Aphinx are fine. They always together.</p>\r\n<p>Tumo is active. He like to swing on the top of cage, he eats well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>January, 2015</p>\r\n<p>Tumo and his partner Aphinx are doing well. They are actives.</p>\r\n<p>Tumo like also to approach Aphinx for playing</p>\r\n<p>September 2013</p>\r\n<p>camp Pararawen, Muara Teweh, Centre Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>Tumo and his partner Aphinx are fine.</p>\r\n<p>They are actives and eat well their food.</p>','EN'),
