	(52630,400,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Strada is a male gibbon of <em>Hylobates Muelleri muelleri</em>, one of gibbons species who can be found in Kalimantan, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of his birth year : 2009.</p>\r\n<p>Strada was arrived at Kalaweit on february, 27th 2010.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Santuary, Muara Teweh, Central Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>August 2018</p>\r\n<p>Strada is fine. He is now with a female gibbon name Poltan. They are just fine.</p>\r\n<p>February 2016.</p>\r\n<p>Strada and Smickey are fine.</p>\r\n<p>Strada swing and scream a lot when there is human near the cage. Strada doesn\'t like human.</p>\r\n<p>August 2015</p>\r\n<p>Poltan was separated from Strada and Smickey.</p>\r\n<p>July 2015</p>\r\n<p>Strada and his friends Smickey and Poltan are doing well.</p>\r\n<p>Strada play a lot with Poltan.</p>\r\n<p>February 2014</p>\r\n<p>Strada is now with Smickey and Poltan.</p>\r\n<p>March 2013</p>\r\n<p>Strada is now alone in the cage.</p>\r\n<p>February, 26th 2012</p>\r\n<p>It\'s a sad day for Strada and Smickey, Michelle was died because of hepatitis.</p>\r\n<p>March 2011</p>\r\n<p>Strada have now a new friend name Smickey.</p>\r\n<p>January 2011</p>\r\n<p>Strada was separated from Noa. He is now with another young gibbon name Michelle.</p>\r\n<p>July 2010</p>\r\n<p>Strada and Noa were translocated to our new center in Pararawen, Muara Teweh, Central Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>Strada and Noa are together in the same cage.</p>\r\n<p>March 2010</p>\r\n<p>Strada is fine.</p>\r\n<p>As Strada is still a young gibbon, the veterinary team give him milk.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','EN'),
