	(52910,485,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Boyaha est un m&acirc;le gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;e de gibbons qui vit dans le sud de la rivi&egrave;re Kapuas et &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito &agrave; &nbsp;Born&eacute;o, Indonesie.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance&nbsp;: 2006.</p>\r\n<p>Boyaha est arriv&eacute; &agrave; Kalaweit le 15 juillet 2012.</p>\r\n<p>notes&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Boyaha va bien. Il est encore seul dans la cage. Apr&egrave;s avoir balanc&eacute;, Boyaha aime s&rsquo;asseoir sur une branche &eacute;tendue en arri&egrave;re de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Octobre 2012</p>\r\n<p>Boyaha va bien dans notre refuge au camp Pararawen, Muara Teweh, Borneo Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Boyaha n&rsquo;a pas encore de compagne</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(52911,485,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Boyaha is a male gibbon of <em>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</em>, one of gibbon species who live in south of the Kapuas river and west of the Barito river in &nbsp;Kalimantan, Indonesia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of year birth : 2006.</p>\r\n<p>Boyaha was&nbsp; arrived at Kalaweit in july, 15 2012.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Centrale Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Boyaha is fine. He is active and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Boyaha like to sit on a branch at the back of cage. Sometimes he jump and hang on in the front of cage when we walk near the cage.</p>','EN'),
