	(52965,500,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p><span>Angel est un b&eacute;b&eacute; siamang (&nbsp;<em><span>Symphalangus syndactylus&nbsp;</span></em>) qui vit sur l&rsquo;&icirc;le Sumatera en Indonesie.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angel est n&eacute; le 26 juin 2013 &agrave; Kalaweit.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ses parents Zacky Dewasa et Angkung sont un couple de siamangs dans Kalaweit Programme.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Notes :</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Supayang Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, a l\'ouest de Sumatera.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Mai 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angel va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec ses parents Zacky Dewasa et Angkung et son petit fr&egrave;re Ozy Kecil.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>F&eacute;vrier 2016</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Observation par : Andre.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky&nbsp; Dewasa, Angkung et leur fils Angel et Ozy Kecil &nbsp;vont bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ce mois l&rsquo;observation se passe en regardant les r&eacute;actions de siamangs et gibbons quand il y a humain pr&egrave;s de la cage.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Quand il y a humain pr&egrave;s de la cage, Zacky Dewasa, Angkung et Angel se balancent beaucoup. Ils sautent et frappent aussi le grillage avec leurs pattes. Apr&egrave;s avoir balanc&eacute;, Zacky Dewasa et Angkung nous approchent et nous regardent comme ils attendaient les fruits. Angel reste en haut de la cage. Comme sa m&egrave;re, Angel nous attaque quand nous sommes n&eacute;gligents.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ozy Kecil va s&rsquo;attacher &agrave; sa maman.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung et Angel mangent bien les fruits.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Decembre 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Le 03 decembre 2015 Angkung a donn&eacute; naissance &agrave; un b&eacute;b&eacute; siamang. C\'est un m&acirc;le. Nous appellons le b&eacute;b&eacute; Ozy.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angkung et son bebe vont bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Janvier 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angel et ses parents vont bien. Ils sont actifs a se balancer, a chanter et a jouer ensemble.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Janvier 2014</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et sa famille vont bien. Ils sont actifs &agrave; se balancer et &agrave; jouer.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa aime s&rsquo;approcher de sa compagne pour jouer. Il attrape et tire Angkung. Puis il court quand Angkung veut l&rsquo;attraper.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et Angkung jouent aussi en se mordant.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angel s&rsquo;attache encore souvent &agrave; sa maman. Parfois il&nbsp; se de&eacute;tache un peu et apprend &agrave; se balancer &agrave; une branche etendue. Mais il reste pr&egrave;s de sa maman.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Zacky Dewasa et Angkung mangent bien les fruits et la nourriture suplementaire comme poulet, oeuf dur et lait.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Juin 2013</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angel va bien. Sa maman s&rsquo;occupe bien de Angel.</span></p>','FR'),
	(52966,500,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7097730251498254\">Angel is a baby Siamang (<em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em>) from Ile Sumatera, Indonesia.</span></div>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.730262067538223\">Angel was born on June 26, 2013 at Kalaweit.</span></p>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9323242270195267\">His parents Zacky Dewasa and Angkung are a couple of siamangs in Kalaweit program.</span></div>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9370852467770614\">Observations :</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5133083220512143\">Supayang Conservation Centre and Sanctuary, Solok, west of Sumatera.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>May 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Angel is fine. He is always with his parents Zacky Dewasa and Angkung and his little brother Ozy Kecil.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.07665818377460742\">February 2016</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9490724565357197\">Observation by: Andre.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9313984016402819\">Zacky Dewasa, Angkung and their son Angel and Ozzie Kecil are fine.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4085251105418197\">This month the observation happens by looking at the reactions of siamangs and Gibbons when there is human near the cage.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4329720425398551\">When there is human near the cage, Zacky Dewasa, Angkung and Angel sway a lot. They jump and also hit the fence with their paws. After swinging, zacky Dewasa and Angkung approach us and look at us as they waited for the fruit. Angel stays at the top of the cage. Like his mother, Angel attacks us when we\'re careless.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.264092549347393\">Ozzie Kecil will attach himself to his mother.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3596111116247558\">Zacky Dewasa, Angkung and Angel eat the fruit well.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.9520525717609476\">December 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7847932856551971\">On December 03, 2015 Angkung gave birth to a baby. He\'s a male. We call the Bebe Ozzie.</span><span id=\"noHighlight_0.5659528916660566\"> Angkung and her baby are fine.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.4490145708404074\">January 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.375599309534253\">Angel and her parents are fine. They are active in swinging, singing and playing together.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.16594216178105736\">January 2014</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.810411114781784\">Zacky Dewasa and his family are fine. They are active in swinging and playing.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.06883173515125385\">Zacky Dewasa likes to get close to his partner to play. He catches and shoots Angkung. Then he runs when Angkung wants to catch him.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.789650768275246\">Zacky Dewasa and Angkung also play by biting.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.22851257648499324\">Angel still often clings to his mom. Sometimes it comes off a bit and learns to swing to an extended branch. But he\'s still near his mom.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"noHighlight_0.06237873967287544\">Zacky Dewasa and Angkung eat well the fruits and food aditional as chicken, hard-boiled egg and milk.</span></p>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.22382777679940702\">June 2013</span></div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.3564256880949631\">Angel\'s fine. His mom looks after Angel.</span></div>','EN'),
