	(53008,512,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p><span>Marcha est une femelle &nbsp;gibbon qui est n&eacute;e dans notre centre de Pararawen &agrave; Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o Centre, Indonesie.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Marcha est n&eacute;e le 15 avril 2014.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Macrha appartient &agrave;l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em><span>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</span></em><span class=\"apple-converted-space\">, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;ile Born&eacute;o.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>Son carnet :</p>\r\n<p><span>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o centre.</span></p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p><span>Marcha et ses parent vont tous bien. Marcha est active et mange bien les fruits.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Marcha aime aussi s\'approcher de son papa Bambang pour jouer.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Janvier 2016</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Marcha et ses parents Bambang et Cimeng vont bien. Ils sont actifs et mangent bien les fruits.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Janvier 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Marcha va bien. Elle est active&nbsp;&agrave; se balancer et&nbsp;&agrave; jouer sur les cordes. Mais elle reste toujours aupr&egrave;s de sa maman. Elle pleure quand Cimeng se balance loin d\'elle.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Avril 2014</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Le 15 avril 2014</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Marcha est n&eacute;e. Cimeng s&rsquo;occupe bien de Marcha.</span></p>','FR'),
	(53009,512,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Marcha is a young gibbon &nbsp;of species&nbsp;<em>Hylobates agilis albibarbis,</em> one of gibbons species who live in Kalimantan island, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Marcha was bornt on Avril, 15 2014 at our center in Pararawen, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan Central.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan central.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Marcha and her parents are doing well. Marcha is active and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Marcha likes also playing with her father Bambang.</p>\r\n<p>January 2016</p>\r\n<p>Marcha and her parents Bambang and Cimeng are doing well. They are actives and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>January 2015</p>\r\n<p>Marcha is doing well. Now she is more activeto &nbsp;swing and play near her mother.</p>\r\n<p>Marcha cry when Cimeng swings far from her.</p>','EN'),
