	(53016,514,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Jelita est un b&eacute;b&eacute; gibbon de l&rsquo;&icirc;le Borneo, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>Jelita est n&eacute;e le 10 juin 2014 dans notre refuge qui se trouve&nbsp;&agrave; Pararawen, Muara Teweh, Borneo centre.</p>\r\n<p>Les parents de Jelita, Djano et Rita, sont un couple de gibbons dans Kalaweit Programme.</p>\r\n<p>notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>Avril&nbsp; 2018</p>\r\n<p>Jelita va bien. Elle est toujours ensemble avec ses parents Djano et Rita.</p>\r\n<p>Jelita est active et mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Fevrier 2016</p>\r\n<p>Jelita et ses parents vont bien. Ils sont actifs et mangent bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Mars 2015</p>\r\n<p>Jelita va bien. Elle est maintenant tres active a se balancer et a jouer.</p>\r\n<p>Juin 2014</p>\r\n<p>Jelita va bien. Rita, sa maman, s&rsquo;occupe bien de Jelita.</p>','FR'),
	(53017,514,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Jelita is a baby gibbon from Borneo, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Jelita was born on June, 10 2014 at our sanctuary in Pararawen, Muara Teweh, Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>Jelita parents, Djano and Rita, are a couple of gibbons in Kalaweit Programme.</p>\r\n<p>notes:</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan Centrale.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Jelita is just fine. She is always with her parents Djano and Rita.</p>\r\n<p>Jelita is active and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>February 2016</p>\r\n<p>Jelita and her parents are doing well. They are actives and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>June 2014</p>\r\n<p>Jelita is fine. Her mother, Rita, take care Jelita with love.</p>','EN'),
