	(53035,519,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Boly est un b&eacute;b&eacute; gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates muelleri muelleri</em> qui est n&eacute; dans notre centre de Pararawen &agrave; Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o.</p>\r\n<p>Boly est n&eacute;e le 21 juin 2014.</p>\r\n<p>Les parents de Boly s&rsquo;appellent Boyke et Liar.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018</p>\r\n<p>Boly va bien. Elle est toujours ensemble avec ses parents.</p>\r\n<p>Ao&ucirc;t 2017</p>\r\n<p>Boly va bien. Elle est active &agrave; se balancer et &agrave; grimper le grillage.</p>\r\n<p>Mars 2015</p>\r\n<p>Boly va bien. Elle est maintenant plus active &agrave; se balancer et &agrave; jouer. Boly joue beaucoup avec sa maman. Mais parfois son papa Boyke aime aussi l\'approcher et l\'attraper pour jouer.</p>\r\n<p>Septembre 2014</p>\r\n<p>Boly va bien. Sa mere, Liar, s&rsquo;occupe bien de Boly.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span><br /></span></p>','FR'),
	(53036,519,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Boly is a baby gibbon who was born in our center at Pararawen, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan Centrale.</p>\r\n<p>Boly was born in june, 21st 2014.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan Centrale.</p>\r\n<p>May 2018</p>\r\n<p>Boly is fine. She is always with her parents Boyke and Liar.</p>\r\n<p>August 2017</p>\r\n<p>Boly is&nbsp; fine. She is active. Like her parents, Boly spends a lot of time at the top of the cage.</p>\r\n<p>March 2015</p>\r\n<p>Boly is now more active. She also plays with her mom Liar. Sometimes her father Boyke approaches and catches Boly for fun.</p>\r\n<p>September 2014</p>\r\n<p>Boly is fine. Her mother takes care of Boly.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','EN'),
