	(53046,640,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Macca est une femelle gibbon de l\'esp&egrave;ces&nbsp;<em>Hylobates klossi</em>, une esp&egrave;e de gibbon qui vit sur l\'&icirc;le de Mentawai&nbsp;&agrave; &nbsp;Sumatera en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L\'estimation de l\'ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2017.</p>\r\n<p>Macca est arriv&eacute;e Kalaweit le 14 octobre 2017.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, &agrave; l\'ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018</p>\r\n<p>Macca va bien. Elle est active et mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53047,640,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Macca is a female gibbon of species <em>Hylobates klossi</em>, one of gibbons species who only can be found in Mentawai island.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of her birth year : 2017.</p>\r\n<p>Macca was arrived at Kalaweit in October, 14 2017.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Center and Santuary, Solok, West Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018</p>\r\n<p>Macca is fine. She is active and eat well the fruits.</p>','EN'),
