	(53066,526,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Lanang est un m&acirc;le gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit au sud de la rivi&egrave;re Kapuas et &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito, Borneo, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2004</p>\r\n<p>Lanang a &eacute;t&eacute; confisqu&eacute; par le d&eacute;partement forestier Indonesien BKSDA.</p>\r\n<p>Nous avons accueilli Lanang le 25 juillet 2014.</p>\r\n<p>L\'examen d\'une prise de sang : Lanang est sain.</p>\r\n<p>notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018</p>\r\n<p>Lanang va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec sa compagne Beta.</p>\r\n<p>Il est actif et mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Le 26 septembre 2016</p>\r\n<p>Lanang est mis ensemble avec une femelle gibbon qui s\'appelle Beta.</p>\r\n<p>Heureusement Lanang et Beta ne sont pas agressifs. Ils peuvent &ecirc;tre ensemble dans une m&ecirc;me cage et manger les fruits sans intimidation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>','FR'),
	(53067,526,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Lanang is a male gibbon,<em> Hylobates agilis albibarbis </em>species, one of species gibbons who lives in the south of the Kapus river and west of the Barito river, Kalimantan, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Year of birth (estimation) : 2004.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The result of blood test : Lanang is clean.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>History :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We received Lanang on july 2th5 2014. He was confiscated by the departement of forests of Indonesia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Like many other wild animals, Lanang was kept as a pet, but he was not... He has spent many years with humans.</p>\r\n<p>Now with Kalaweit, he has a chance to be released in the forest. But before this Lanang must spend some years of rehabilitation in our center.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Santuary, Muara Teweh, Central Kalimantan.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>May 2018</p>\r\n<p>Lanang and his partner Beta are fine. They are actives and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>September, 26 2016</p>\r\n<p>Lanang is now together with a female gibbon name Beta. They are just fine.</p>','EN'),
