	(53094,533,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Baffie est un b&eacute;b&eacute; gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&eacute;ce&nbsp;<em>Hylobates muelleri muelleri</em><em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons </em>&nbsp;qui vit dans le nord de la rivi&egrave;re Kapuas et &agrave; l&rsquo;est de la riv&egrave;re Barito &agrave; sur Born&eacute;o, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>Baffie est n&eacute; dans notre centre de Pararawen le 03 mars 2015.</p>\r\n<p>Les parents de Baffie, Roland et Juliet sont un couple dans Kalaweit Programme.</p>\r\n<p>notes&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Le 29 avril 2018 Juliet a donn&eacute; naissance&nbsp;&agrave; un b&eacute;b&eacute; gibbon. Nous appellons son b&eacute;b&eacute; Rolie.</p>\r\n<p>January 2018</p>\r\n<p>Baffie va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec ses parents.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2016</p>\r\n<p>Baffie et ses parents vont tous bien. Ils sont actifs et mangent&nbsp; bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Mars 2015</p>\r\n<p>Le 03 mars 2015</p>\r\n<p>Baffie est ne&hellip; Juliet sa maman s&rsquo;occupe bien de Baffie</p>\r\n<p><span><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span><br /></span></p>','FR'),
	(53095,533,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p><span>Baffie is a baby gibbon of species <em>Hylobates Muelleri muelleri</em>, a gibbon specy that lives in the north of Kapuas river and in the east of Barito river &nbsp;in Kalimantan , Indonesia.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Baffie was born in our center at Pararawen on march, 3 2015.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Notes :</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Pararawen Conservation Center and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan Centrale.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Avril, 29 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Juliet give birth to a baby gibbon. We call her baby Rolie.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>January 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Baffie is fine. He is always with his parents.</span></p>\r\n<p>January 2017</p>\r\n<p>Baffie and his parents are just fine. He is active and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Baffie spend a lot of time with his mother Juliet.</p>\r\n<p>January 2016</p>\r\n<p>Baffie and his parents Roland and Juliet are doing well. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','EN'),
