	(53105,536,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p><span>Atan est un m&acirc;le gibbon&nbsp; de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em><span>Hylobates Agilis albibarbis</span></em><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><em>,</em> l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur </span>&nbsp;l&rsquo;ile Born&eacute;o, Indonesie.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance&nbsp;: 2007</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Atan est recuper&eacute; dans une ville &agrave; Kapuas, Born&eacute;o Centre, le 21 avril 2015.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>L&rsquo;examen medical :</span></p>\r\n<p><span>son carnet&nbsp;:</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o Centre.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Mars 2016</span></p>\r\n<p>Le 29 mars 2016 Atan est tomb&eacute; malade. Il est ensuite amen&eacute; &agrave; la clinique pour des soins.</p>\r\n<p>Sa temp&eacute;rature est &eacute;lev&eacute;e de 40, 1 degr&eacute;</p>\r\n<p>Le 30 mars 2016, dans l&rsquo;apr&egrave;s &ndash; midi, Atan nous a quitt&eacute;...</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;autopsie : il y a des d&eacute;gradations dans sa foie et son poumon</p>\r\n<p>La cause de son d&eacute;c&egrave;s : Pour le moment nous ne savons pas exactement la cause du d&eacute;c&egrave;s de Atan.</p>\r\n<p><span>Janvier 2016</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Atan va bien. Il est actif et mange bien les fruits.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Le 22 avril 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Atan est transfer&eacute;&nbsp; &nbsp;&agrave; notre nouveau centre de Pararawen &agrave; &nbsp;Muara Teweh.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Atan va bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Il est plac&eacute; pour un moment dans une cage de quarantaine.</span></p>','FR'),
	(53106,536,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Atan is a male gibbon of species <em>Hylobates Agilis albibarbis</em>, one of gibbons species who live in Kalimantan, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of birth year : 2007.</p>\r\n<p>Medicale examination :</p>\r\n<p>Atan was saved at Kapuas, Kalimantan Centrale, on avril, 21 2015.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan Centrale.</p>\r\n<p>March, 28 2016 Atan was sick. We have to take care Atan in the clinic. His body temperature was high 40, 1</p>\r\n<p>March, 29 2016 in the afternoon Atan pass away...</p>\r\n<p>Autopsy ; we found his heart and lung were damage.</p>\r\n<p>For a moment we don&rsquo;t know exactly what disease due to Atan death</p>\r\n<p>January 2016</p>\r\n<p>Atan is just fine. He is active and eat well the fruits.</p>','EN'),
