	(53123,541,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p><span>Simon est un m&acirc;le gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em><span>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</span></em><span class=\"apple-converted-space\">, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbon qui vit dans le sud de la rivi&egrave;re Kapuas et &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito &agrave; </span>Kalimantan, Indonesie.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance&nbsp;: n&eacute;e en 2014.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Confisqu&eacute;e&nbsp;&agrave; : Palangkaraya, Kalimantan Centrale par l&rsquo;aide de D&eacute;partement Forestier et de la souce naturelle ( BKSDA ).</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Arriv&eacute;e dans Kalaweit Programme&nbsp;: le 14 janvier 2015.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Histoire :</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Comme beaucoup d&rsquo;autres gibbons, Simon a &eacute;t&eacute; vendu comme un animal de compagnie. Il vit alors avec l&rsquo;homme loin de sa famille et la for&ecirc;t.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Maintenant &agrave; Kalaweit, Simon a de la chance d&rsquo;&ecirc;tre rel&acirc;ch&eacute; dans la for&ecirc;t. Mais il doit d&rsquo;abord passer quelques ann&eacute;es de r&eacute;habilitation dans notre centre.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Notes&nbsp;:</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Pararawen&nbsp; Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan Centrale.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Juin 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Simon va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec Aliya. Ils sont actifs et mangent bien les fruits.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ao&ucirc;t &nbsp;2017</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Simon et Aliya vont bien. Elles passent aussi de temps &agrave; jouer ensemble. Elles se poursuivent et s&rsquo;attrapent en haut et en bas de la cage.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ao&ucirc;t 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Le 15 ao&ucirc;t 2015, un jour triste pour Aliya et Simon, Obok est d&eacute;ced&eacute;e. Obok est tomb&eacute;e malade. Pendant 2 jours elle n&rsquo;a pas &eacute;te active comme d&rsquo;habitude et n&rsquo;a pas bien mang&eacute; les fruits.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>L&rsquo;autopsie : l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe v&eacute;t&eacute;rinaire nous a conclu que la cause du d&eacute;c&egrave;s de Obok est par des infections&nbsp; septisemia ( septicaemia ).</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Mars 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Simon va bien. Elle est maintenant avec Obok et Aliya, deux autres jeunes gibbons. Ils s\'entendent bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span><br /></span></p>','FR'),
	(53124,541,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Simon is a male gibbon of <em>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</em>, one of gibbon species who live in south of the Kapuas river and west of the Barito river in Kalimantan, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p><span>Estimation of his birth year : 2014.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Simon was confiscated by the departement foresty of Indonesia. We received Simon on january, 14 2015.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>History :</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Like many others gibbons, Simon was sold like a pet. He live with human far away from his family and forest.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Now with Kalaweit, Simon have a chance to be release in the forest. But he must pass some years of rehabilitation in our center.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Notes :</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Pararawen Conservation Center and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Central Kalimantan.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>June 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Simon is fine. He is always with Aliya. They are actives and eat well the fruits.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>August 2017</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Simon is doing well. He is always with his partner Aliya.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>They are actives and like to play in the cage.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.7369836970280736\">March 2015</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span id=\"noHighlight_0.11994300430438898\">Simon\'s fine. He is now with Obok and Aliya, two other young gibbons. They get along well.</span></div>\r\n</div>','EN'),
