	(53135,544,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p><span>Bori est un b&eacute;b&eacute; gibbon d&rsquo;un couple des gibbons dans Kalaweit Programme &agrave; Borneo.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Bori est n&eacute;e le 06 juin 2015.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ses parents Karibou et Bona sont les gibbons de l&rsquo;espece<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em><span>Hylobates Muelleri muelleri.</span></em><span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>L&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit dans le sud &ndash; est de Kalimantan, approximativement dans le sud de la rivi&egrave;re Mahakam et &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>notes&nbsp;:</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ao&ucirc;t&nbsp; 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Bori va bien. Elle est toujous ensemble avec sa famille.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Ao&ucirc;t 2017</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Bori et sa famille vont tous bien. Elle joue beaucoup avec son grand fr&egrave;re Boka.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Mai 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Bori va bien. Bona s&rsquo;occupe bien de Bori.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Bori a un fr&egrave;re qui s&rsquo;appelle Boka.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>','FR'),
	(53136,544,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Bori was born on Kalaweit Programme in Borneo.</p>\r\n<p><span>Bori was born on june, 6th 2015.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Like her parents Karibou and Bona, Bori belongs to specy<em><span>Hylobates Muelleri muelleri</span></em>. A specy that can be found in the southeast of Kalimantan, Indonesia. This specy lives in the south of Mahakam river and west of the Barito river.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Notes :</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Pararawen Conservation Center and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan Central.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>August&nbsp; 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Bori is fine. She is always with her family.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>August 2017</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Bori and her family are doing well. Bori likes to play with his older brother Boka on the top of cage.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>May 2015</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Bori is fine. Bona takes care well of Bori.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>Bori has also a brother named Boka.</span></p>','EN'),
