	(53160,635,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Frengky est un m&acirc;le gibbon qui&nbsp; appartient &agrave; l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates muelleri muelleri</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit dans le sud &ndash; est de&nbsp; Born&eacute;o, approximativement au sud de la rivi&egrave;re de Mahakam&nbsp; et dans l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito <em>.</em></p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2015.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;histoire :</p>\r\n<p>Frengky a&nbsp; &eacute;t&eacute; aussi un des victimes de la d&eacute;forestation et du trafic animaux sauvages.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Frengky&nbsp; va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec son ami Azril.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53161,635,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Frengky is a male gibbon of species <em>Hylobates muelleri muelleri</em>, one of gibbon species who live in the southeast of Kalimantan, Indonesia approximately south of the Mahakam river and west of the Barito river.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation oh his birth year : 2015.</p>\r\n<p>History :</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Santuary, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Frengky is doing well. He is always with his friend Azril.</p>','EN'),
