	(53175,555,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Cess est un m&acirc;le&nbsp; gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce&nbsp;<em>Hylobates Muelleri muelleri</em>, l&rsquo;une d&rsquo;esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;ile Born&eacute;o, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2011.</p>\r\n<p>Le resultat des prises de sang : Cess est sain.</p>\r\n<p>Cess a &eacute;t&eacute; sauv&eacute; par le departement forestier de Muara Teweh au Centre Borneo le 21 novembre 2015.</p>\r\n<p>notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Borneo centrale.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Cess va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec son ami Ipul.</p>\r\n<p>Ils jouent beaucoup ensemble.</p>\r\n<p>Juillet 2016</p>\r\n<p>Cess est maintenant avec un autre jeune male gibbon qui s\'appelle Ipul. Ils vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Fin de mars 2016</p>\r\n<p>Cess est maintenant avec Pochi. Pochi a encore peur de Cess. Elle se deplace quand Cess vient s\'approcher.</p>\r\n<p>Mars 2016</p>\r\n<p>Cess est maintenant ensemble avec un autre male gibbon qui s\'appelle Tompel. Ils vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Fevrier 2016</p>\r\n<p>Cess va bien. Il est actif et mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Decembre 2015</p>\r\n<p>Cess va bien.</p>','FR'),
	(53176,555,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Cess is a male gibbon of <em>Hylobates muelleri muelleri</em>, one of gibbon species who live in Kalimantan, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of his birth year&nbsp;: 2011.</p>\r\n<p>History&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<p>Cess was saved by the departement foresty of Muara Teweh on november, 21 2015.</p>\r\n<p>He was captured in the wild and lived with human as pet for years.</p>\r\n<p>Now with Kalaweit, Cess can live with others gibbons and have a chance to be release in the forest. But for this, he must pass some years of rehabilitation in our center.</p>\r\n<p>Notes&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Santuary, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Cess is doing well. He is always with his friend Ipul.</p>\r\n<p>july 2016</p>\r\n<p>Cess is now with another male gibbon name Ipul. They are just fine.</p>','EN'),
