	(53206,563,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Ruth est une femelle gibbon de l\'esp&egrave;ce&nbsp;<em>Hylobates Agilis albibarbis</em>, l\'une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l\'&icirc;le de Borneo en Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>L\'estimation de l\'ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2008.</p>\r\n<p>Ruth a &eacute;t&eacute; sauv&eacute;e le 08 septembre 2015 dans une ville de Palangkaraya, Borneo centre.</p>\r\n<p>Comme l\'histoire des autres animaux sauvages qui sont captures dans leur milieu naturel, Ruth est detenue comme un animal de compagnie chez humain pendant des annees.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Borneo Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Ruth va bien. Elle est toujours ensemble avec son compagnon Feri.</p>\r\n<p>F&eacute;vrier 2017</p>\r\n<p>Ruth va bien. Elle est maintenant ensemble avec un male gibbon qui s\'appelle Feri.</p>\r\n<p>Ruth a encore peur de s\'approcher de Feri.</p>','FR'),
	(53207,563,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Ruth is a female gibbon of <em>Hylobates Agilis albibarbis</em>, one of gibbons species who live in Kalimantan, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of her birth year : 2008.</p>\r\n<p>Ruth was saved on september, 8 2015 in Palangkaraya.</p>\r\n<p>Like many others wild animals, Ruth was considered as a pet for many years. She lost her family and her forest.</p>\r\n<p>Now with Kalaweit, she can have contacts with others gibbons and can be released in the forest again. But for this Ruth must wait some years of rehabilitation in our center.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Santuary, Muara Teweh, Central Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Ruth is doing well. She is always with her partner Feri.</p>\r\n<p>February 2017</p>\r\n<p>Ruth is now with a male gibbon name Feri.</p>','EN'),
