	(53220,567,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Anis est un m&acirc;le gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates Muelleri muelleri</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;ile de Born&eacute;o, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2011.</p>\r\n<p>Anis &nbsp;a &eacute;t&eacute; sauv&eacute; le 16 janvier 2015 dans une grande ville Palangkaraya, la capitale du Borneo centre.</p>\r\n<p>Comme l&rsquo;histoire des autres animaux sauvages qui sont captur&eacute;s dans leur milieu naturel, Anis est d&eacute;tenu comme un animal de compagnie chez humain.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Notes t :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Borneo Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018</p>\r\n<p>Anis va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec sa compagne Unyil.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2017</p>\r\n<p>Anis et Unyil vont bien. Ils sont actifs et mangent bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Anis et Unyil passent aussi de temps &agrave; jouer.&nbsp;Ils se poursuivent et se frappent en bas et en haut de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Mars 2016</p>\r\n<p>Anis est maintenant ensemble avec une autre femelle gibbon qui s\'appelle Unyil Borneo. Ils vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53221,567,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Anis is a male &nbsp;gibbon of species <em>Hylobate Muelleri muelleri</em>, one of gibbon species in the world who live in Borneo, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of his birth ; 2011.</p>\r\n<p>Anis was saved in January 2015 in Palangkaraya City, Borneo Central.</p>\r\n<p>Like many others stories of wild animal, Anis was kept as a pet. Far from her home, the forest, and her species. People are blind and not really sensitive to what this wild animal needs.</p>\r\n<p>Observations :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>May 2018</p>\r\n<p>Anis is fine. He is always with his partner Unyil.</p>\r\n<p>January 2017</p>\r\n<p>Anis and Unyil are doing well. They are actives and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Anis and Unyil like also play together, They poursue and catch each other.</p>\r\n<p>May 2016</p>\r\n<p>Anis is now with another young female gibbon name Unyil Borneo. They are just fine.</p>\r\n<p>Anis is just fine. He is for a while alone in the cage.</p>','EN'),
