	(53253,576,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Unyil Borneo est une femelle gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce<em> Hylobates Muelleri muelleri</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;ile Born&eacute;o, Indonesie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance ; 2012.</p>\r\n<p>Le resultat d&rsquo;une prise de sang : Unyil est saine.</p>\r\n<p>Unyil Borneo a &eacute;t&eacute; sauv&eacute;e le 11 ao&ucirc;t 2015 dans une ville &agrave; Muara Teweh, Borneo centre.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018</p>\r\n<p>Unyil va bien. Elle est toujours ensemble avec son compagnon Anis.</p>\r\n<p>Unyil est active et mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Mars 2016</p>\r\n<p>Unyil est maintenant avec un autre male &nbsp;gibbon qui s\'appelle Anis. Ils vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2016</p>\r\n<p>Unyil &nbsp;Borneo est maintenant ensemble avec un autre jeune male gibbon qui s&rsquo;appelle Tompel. Ils ont du m&ecirc;me age.</p>\r\n<p>Unyil Borneo et tompel vont bien.</p>','FR'),
	(53254,576,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Unyil Borneo is a young female gibbon of Borneo.</p>\r\n<p>Year of her birth : 2012.</p>\r\n<p>Unyil Borneo was saved on August 2015 in the village at Muara Teweh, Borneo Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Observations :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Borneo Centre.</p>\r\n<p>May 2018</p>\r\n<p>Unyil and her partner Anis are doing well, they are actives and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Unyil and Anis like to play together. They catch and pull each other arm or legs.</p>\r\n<p>May 2016</p>\r\n<p>Unyil is now with another male gibbon named Anis, they are fine.</p>\r\n<p>January 2016</p>\r\n<p>Unyil is now with another young male gibbon name Tompel. They have the same age.</p>','EN'),
