	(53257,577,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Ozy Kecil est un b&eacute;b&eacute; siamang &nbsp;( <em>Symphalangus Syndactylus</em> ) qui est n&eacute; dans notre centre de Supayang, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Ozy Kecil est le b&eacute;b&eacute; d&rsquo;un couple de siamangs, Zacky Dewasa et Angkung.</p>\r\n<p>Ozy Kecil est n&eacute; le 03 decembre 2015.</p>\r\n<p>Observations :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Santuaire, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018</p>\r\n<p>Ozy Kecil va bien. Il est toujours ensemble avec ses parents and his brother Angel.</p>\r\n<p>Observation mois : Janvier 2017</p>\r\n<p>Observation sur terrain par : Andre.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung et leur deux fils Angel et Ozy vont tous bien.</p>\r\n<p>Ils sont actifs &agrave; se balancer, &agrave; chanter et &agrave; jouer ensemble dans la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa, Angel et Ozy aiment jouer ensemble. Ils se poursuivent, se frappent et se mordent. Angkung ne jouent pas beaucoup avec son compagnon et ses fils. Elle aime s&rsquo;asseoir dans l&rsquo;une des cabanes.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung, Angel et Ozy mangent&nbsp; bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Quand l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe vient pour donner les fruits, Zacky Dewasa et Angkung se balancent beaucoup afin de redescendre et prendre les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Angel aime suspendre et regarde l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe en haut de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Ozy va s&rsquo;attacher &agrave; sa papa.</p>\r\n<p>Angel et Ozy prennent et mangent les fruits quand l&rsquo;&eacute;quipe est loin de la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Decembre 2015</p>\r\n<p>Ozy Kecil va bien. Sa mere s&rsquo;occupe bien de Ozy.</p>','FR'),
	(53258,577,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<div id=\"destText\" class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">\r\n<p>Ozy &nbsp;Kecil is a baby Siamang (<em>Symphalangus Syndactylus</em>) who was born in our center of Supayang, Solok, west of Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Ozy Kecil is the baby of a couple of siamangs, Zacky Dewasa and Angkung.</p>\r\n<p>Ozy Kecil was born on 03 December 2015.</p>\r\n<p>Observations:</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre and Sanctuary, Solok, west of Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>May 2018</p>\r\n<p>Ozy Kecil is fine. He is always together with his brother Angel and his parents Zacky Dewasa and Angkung.</p>\r\n<p>January 2017</p>\r\n<p>Observation&nbsp;by: Andre.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung and their two sons Angel and Ozy all go well.</p>\r\n<p>They are active in swinging, singing and playing together in the cage.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa, Angel and Ozy like to play together. They continue, they hit each other and they bite each other. Angkung do not play much with his companion and his sons. She likes to sit in one of the huts.</p>\r\n<p>Zacky Dewasa, Angkung, Angel and Ozzie eat the fruit well.</p>\r\n<p>When the team comes to give the fruit, Zacky Dewasa and Angkung sway a lot in order to come down and take the fruit.</p>\r\n<p>Angel likes to hang out and watch the team at the top of the cage.</p>\r\n<p>Ozzie will attach himself to his papa.</p>\r\n<p>Angel and Ozzie take and eat the fruit when the team is away from the cage.</p>\r\n<p>December 2015</p>\r\n<p>Ozzie Kecil is fine. Her mother takes good care of Ozzie.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"textArea\" style=\"direction: ltr;\">&nbsp;</div>','EN'),
