	(53327,596,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Kitiw est une femelle gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates muelleri muelleri</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces des gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;&icirc;le Born&eacute;o, en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2010.</p>\r\n<p>Kitiw a &eacute;t&eacute; sauv&eacute;e dans un petit village &agrave; &nbsp;Kandui le 18 octobre 2016.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;histoire :</p>\r\n<p>Kitiw a aussi &eacute;t&eacute; l&rsquo;une des victimes de la cruaut&eacute; de l&rsquo;homme envers les animaux sauvages et la nature.&nbsp; L&rsquo;homme l&rsquo;a attrap&eacute;e et l&rsquo;a enferm&eacute;e dans une petite cage quand elle &eacute;tait encore tout petit.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Ao&ucirc;t 2018</p>\r\n<p>Kitiw est maintenant plus active dans la cage. Elle se d&eacute;place maintenant en dehors de la cabane. Avant elle &eacute;tait timide et a eu peur de Tompel.</p>\r\n<p>Ao&ucirc;t 2017</p>\r\n<p>Kitiw est maintenant ensemble avec un male gibbon qui s\'appelle Tompel. Kitiw a encore un peu peur de Tompel.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53328,596,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Kitiw is a female gibbon of <em>Hylobates Muelleri muelleri</em>, one of gibbons species who can be found in Kalimantan, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of her birth year : 2010.</p>\r\n<p>Kiwit was saved in a small village near our center on October, 18 2016.</p>\r\n<p>Like many others wild animal, Kitiw was also victim of deforestation in Kalimantan, she lost her forest and family. People threat Kitiw as a pet.</p>\r\n<p>Now wih Kalaweit she can live with others gibbons and have a chance to be back again in the forest. But Kitiw must pass&eacute; some years of rehabilitation in our center.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Santuary, Muara Teweh, Central Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>August 2018</p>\r\n<p>Kitiw is fine. She is always with her partner Tompel.</p>\r\n<p>August 2017</p>\r\n<p>Kitiw is now with a male gibbon name Tompel.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','EN'),
