	(53362,606,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Jodi est un m&acirc;le siamang ( <em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em> ), l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de singes qui vit sur l&rsquo;ile de Sumatera en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2012.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;histoire :</p>\r\n<p>Jodi a &eacute;t&eacute; sauv&eacute; le 22 decembre 2016 &agrave; Bogor, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Java.</p>\r\n<p>Comme beaucoup d&rsquo;autres siamangs et gibbons dans notre centre de rehabilitation, Jodi a de la chance d&rsquo;&ecirc;tre rel&acirc;ch&eacute; dans la for&ecirc;t. Pour arriver &agrave; ce but, Jodi doit passer quelques &eacute;tapes de rehabilitation qui peuvent prendre des ann&eacute;es.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Jodi va bien. Il est encore seul dans la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Juin 2017</p>\r\n<p>Jodi&nbsp; va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Il est actif et mange bien les fruits.</p>','FR'),
	(53363,606,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Jodi Sumatera is a male siamang ( <em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em> ), one of gibbons species who can be found in Sumatera, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of his birth year : 2012.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>History :</p>\r\n<p>Jodi Sumatera was saved on december, 22 2016 in Bogor, West Java.</p>\r\n<p>Like many others wild animals, Jodi Sumatera was a victim of wild animal traffic. He was sold like a pet.</p>\r\n<p>Now with Kalaweit, Jodi Sumatera have a chance to live with anothers siamangs and &nbsp;can be release in the forest. But he must wait some years of rehabilitation in our center.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Cente and Santuary, Solok, West Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>January 2018</p>\r\n<p>Jodi Sumatera is doing well. He is stil alone.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','EN'),
