	(53377,610,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Boni est un m&acirc;le gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce&nbsp;<em>Hylobates</em><em> a</em><em>gilis albibarbis</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces des gibbons qui vit dans le sud de la rivi&egrave;re Kapuas et &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito &agrave; Born&eacute;o en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance ; 2010.</p>\r\n<p>Histoire :</p>\r\n<p>Boni a &eacute;t&eacute; sauv&eacute; le 26 janvier 2017 dans la ville de Muara Teweh, Kalimantan centrale.</p>\r\n<p>Comme beaucoup d&rsquo;autres animaux sauvages, Boni a vecu chez les gens comme animal de compagnie.</p>\r\n<p>Maintenant avec Kalaweit, Boni a de la chance d&rsquo;&ecirc;tre rel&acirc;ch&eacute; dans la for&ecirc;t. Mais pour cela il doit d&rsquo;abord passer quelques ann&eacute;es de r&eacute;habilitation dans notre centre.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Born&eacute;o Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Boni va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Il est actif et mange bien les fruits.&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53378,610,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Boni is a male gibbon of species <em>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</em>, one of gibbon species who can be found in south of the Kapusa river and west of the Barito river in Kalimantan, Indonesia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Year of birth year (estimation) : 2010.</p>\r\n<p>History :</p>\r\n<p>Boni was saved on january, 26 2017 in Muara Teweh, a small town located in Kalimantan central.</p>\r\n<p>Like many others wild animals illegaly kept, Boni was kept as a pet by humans.</p>\r\n<p>Now staying at Kalaweit, Boni has a chance to be released in the forest. But before that he must spend some years of rehabilitation in our center.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Santuary, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan central</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Boni is just fine. He is active and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','EN'),
