	(53381,611,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Bastian est jeune m&acirc;le gibbon qui appartient &agrave; l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</em> , l&rsquo;une&nbsp; des esp&egrave;ces des gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;ile de Born&eacute;o en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2016.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;histoire :</p>\r\n<p>Bastian est sauv&eacute; le 27 janvier 2017&nbsp; &agrave; Palangkaraya.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, &agrave; Born&eacute;o Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Bastian est maintenant avec un autre jeune gibbon qui s\'appelle Tanta. Ils vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2018</p>\r\n<p>Bastian et Puput sont maintenant plac&eacute;s ensemble dans une cage &agrave; la clinique.</p>\r\n<p>Bastian &nbsp;est plus dominant. Il aime s&rsquo;approcher ou d&eacute;ranger Puput pour jouer.</p>\r\n<p>Decembre 2017</p>\r\n<p>Bastian est maintenant ensemble avec une jeune femelle gibbon qui s\'appelle Bhayangkari. Ils vont bien.</p>\r\n<p>Janvier 2017</p>\r\n<p>Bastian va bien.&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53382,611,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Bastian is a young male gibbon of species <em>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</em>, one of species gibbons who live in Kalimantan, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Year of birth (estimation) : 2016.</p>\r\n<p>History :</p>\r\n<p>Bastian was rescued in Palangkaraya, Kalimantan Central, on january, 27th 2017.</p>\r\n<p>Like many other wild animals, Bastian was captured in the wild and been kept like a pet animal, in a small cage.</p>\r\n<p>notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Sanctuary, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan Central.</p>\r\n<p>Avril 2018</p>\r\n<p>Bastian is now with another young gibbon name Tanta. They are fine.</p>\r\n<p>January 2018</p>\r\n<p>Bastian is now with another young female gibbon name Puput. They are just fine.</p>\r\n<p>December 2017</p>\r\n<p>Bastian is now with a young female gibbon name Bhayangkari. They are just fine.</p>\r\n<p>Juin 2017</p>\r\n<p>Bastian is doing well. He is active and eat well the fruits.</p>','EN'),
