	(53408,618,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Momo est un jeune femelle siamang ( Symphalangus syndactylus ), l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;ile de Sumatera en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2012.</p>\r\n<p>Momo a &eacute;t&eacute; sauv&eacute;e le 23 mai 2017 dans une ville &agrave; Riau.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;histoire :</p>\r\n<p>Pendant des ann&eacute;es, Momo est trait&eacute;e comme un animal de compagnie. Momo portait de tee &ndash; shirt quand nous le recevons.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Juin 2018</p>\r\n<p>Momo va bien. Elle est active et mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53409,618,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Momo is a young female siamang ( Symphalangus syndactylus ), one of gibbons species who live in Sumatera, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of birth year : 2012.</p>\r\n<p>Momo was sauved on May 23 2017.</p>\r\n<p>History :</p>\r\n<p>For the long years, Momo was considered like a pet animal. He wear a t-shirt when we received him.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Center and Sanctuary, Solok, West Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>June 2018</p>\r\n<p>Momo is just fine. She is active and eat well the fruits.</p>','EN'),
