	(53428,624,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Jenni est une femelle Siamang ( <em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em> ), l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de grandes &nbsp;singes qui vit sur l&rsquo;ile Sumatera en Indon&eacute;sie.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2013.</p>\r\n<p>L\'histoire :</p>\r\n<p>Kalaweit a re&ccedil;u Jenni le 21 juin 2017 du D&eacute;partement Forestier de Jambi.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera</p>\r\n<p>Juin&nbsp; 2018</p>\r\n<p>Jenni va bien. Elle est active et mange bien les fruits.</p>\r\n<p>Juin 2017</p>\r\n<p>Jenni va bien. Elle est pour le moment plac&eacute;e seule dans notre r&eacute;serve &agrave; Supayang.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53429,624,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Jenni is a female siamang ( Symphalangus syndactylus ), one of species big apes who live in Sumatera, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of her birth year : 2013.</p>\r\n<p>History :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Kalaweit received Jenni from The Forest Departement of Jambi on June, 21 2017.</p>\r\n<p>Like many others wild animal, Jenni was one of victimes of deforestation and hunters.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Center and Santuary, Solok, West Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>June 2018</p>\r\n<p>Jenni is fine. She is active and eat well the fruits.</p>\r\n<p>June 2017</p>\r\n<p>Jenni is doing well. She is alone in the cage.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','EN'),
