	(53452,642,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Boci est un b&eacute;b&eacute; siamang ( <em>Symphalangus syndactylus </em>) qui est n&eacute; dans notre centre de Supayang &agrave; Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Boci est n&eacute; le 07 avril 2017.</p>\r\n<p>Ses parents, Cipluk et Bonzo sont un couple de siamangs &agrave; Kalaweit.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Santuaire, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Mai 2018&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Boci va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Comme il a bien grandi. Boci est maintenant tr&egrave;s actif&nbsp;&agrave; se balancer et&nbsp;&agrave; jouer dans la cage avec ses parents.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53453,642,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Boci is a baby siamang ( <em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em> ) who was born in our center in Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Boci was born on avril, 7 2017.</p>\r\n<p>His parents, Cipluk and Bonzo, &nbsp;are a couple of siamangs at Kalaweit.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Center and Santuary, Solok, West Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>May 2018&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Boci is doing well.</p>\r\n<p>He is now active doing his activities like swinging and playing with his parents.&nbsp;</p>','EN'),
