	(53484,639,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Puput est un jeune femelle gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit dans le sud de la rivi&egrave;re Kapuas et &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito &agrave; Born&eacute;o en Indon&eacute;sie.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2016.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Puput a &eacute;t&eacute; confisqu&eacute;e par le departement forestier de Muara Teweh au centre de Born&eacute;o. Elle est arriv&eacute;e &agrave; Kalaweit le 21 octobre 2017.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Comme beaucoup d&rsquo;autres gibbons, Puput est captur&eacute;e dans la nature. L&rsquo;homme a tu&eacute; ses parents. Les grandes compagnies ont d&eacute;truit sa for&ecirc;t. Puput vit alors avec les gens comme un animal de compagnie.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Maintenant avec Kalaweit, Puput vit avec les autres gibbons et a de la chance d&rsquo;&ecirc;tre rel&acirc;ch&eacute;e dans la for&ecirc;t. Mais pour cela elle doit d&rsquo;abord passer quelques ann&eacute;es de rehabilitation dans notre centre.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Notes :</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, au centre de Born&eacute;o.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Avril 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Le 07 avril 2018 Puput est decedee. Elle a eu un accident en jouant sur le hamac. Son cou est etrangle par les cordes du hamac.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">F&eacute;vrier 2018</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Puput va bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">Elle est maintenant ensemble dans une m&ecirc;me cage avec un jeune m&acirc;le gibbon qui s&rsquo;appelle Bastian. Ils s&rsquo;entendent bien.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','FR'),
	(53485,639,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Puput is a female gibbon of <em>Hylobates Agilis albibarbis</em>, one of gibbons species who can be found in the south of Kapuas river and in the west of Barito river in Borneo, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of her birth year : 2016.</p>\r\n<p>Puput was confiscated by the departement foresty of Muara Teweh, Borneo Central. She was arrived in Kalaweit on october, 21 2017.</p>\r\n<p>Puput was captured in&nbsp; the wild. People kill her parents. The big companies destroy her forest. Then she live with human as a pet.</p>\r\n<p>Now with Kalaweit, Puput live with others gibbons and have a chance to be released in the forest again but for this she must wait some years of rehabilitation in our center.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Santuary, Muara Teweh, Borneo Central.</p>\r\n<p>February 2018</p>\r\n<p>Puput is fine. She is now with a young male gibbon name Bastian.</p>','EN'),
