	(53500,647,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Jolien est une femelle siamang <em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;&icirc;le Sumatera en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2009.</p>\r\n<p>Jolien a &eacute;t&eacute; re&ccedil;ue du d&eacute;partement forestier de Sumatera le 15 mars 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Santuaire, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Juillet 2018</p>\r\n<p>Jolien va bien. Elle est encore seule dans la cage.</p>\r\n<p>Jolien est active. Dans le matin, elle chante et se balance.</p>\r\n<p>Jolien passe aussi de temps &agrave; chercher et &agrave; manger des feuilles ou des insectes.</p>\r\n<p>Jolien mange aussi bien les fruits comme les bananes, papaye, mandarin, ananas et pasteque.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53501,647,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Jolien is a female siamang of <em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em>, one of gibbons species who can be found in Sumatera, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of her birth year : 2009.</p>\r\n<p>Jolien was received from the Departement of Foresty Indonesia in Sumatera on march, 15<sup>th</sup> 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Center and Santuary, Solok, West Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>July 2018</p>\r\n<p>Jolien is fine. For a while, she is still alone in the cage.</p>\r\n<p>Jolien is active. In the morning, she sing and swing.</p>\r\n<p>Jolien like also search and eat the leaves or insects.</p>\r\n<p>Jolien eat well the fruits like bananas, pineapple, orange, papaya and water melon.</p>','EN'),
