	(53504,648,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Mang est un m&acirc;le siamang de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;&icirc;le Sumatera en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance ; 2008.</p>\r\n<p>Mang a &eacute;t&eacute; recu du D&eacute;partement Forestier &agrave; Sumatera le 15 mars 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Solok, &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>Juillet 2018</p>\r\n<p>Mang va bien.</p>\r\n<p>Il est ensemble avec sa compagne Ming.</p>\r\n<p>Mang est actif. Dans le matin, il chante et se balance.</p>\r\n<p>Mang passe aussi de temps &agrave; chercher des&nbsp; insectes ou des feuilles.</p>\r\n<p>Mang mange bien les fruits comme les bananes, papaya, ananas, mandarin et pasteque.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','FR'),
	(53505,648,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Mang is a male siamang of species <em>Symphalangus syndactylus</em>, one of gibbons species who live in Sumatera, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of his birth year : 2008.</p>\r\n<p>Mang was received from the Departement of Foresty in Sumatera on march, 15<sup>th</sup> 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Supayang Conservation Center and Santuary, Solok, West Sumatera.</p>\r\n<p>July 2018</p>\r\n<p>Mang is fine. He is together with his partner Ming.</p>\r\n<p>Mang is active. He is swing and sing.</p>\r\n<p>Mang like also searching the insects or leaves.</p>\r\n<p>Mang eat well the fruits like bananas, pineapple, orange, papaya and water melon.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','EN'),
