	(53512,650,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Cacan est une femelle &nbsp;gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates agilis albibarbis</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit sur l&rsquo;&icirc;le Kalimantan en Indon&eacute;sie.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2014.</p>\r\n<p>Cacan a &eacute;t&eacute; sauv&eacute; &agrave; Bintang Linggi, un petit village qui se trouve sur le bord du fleuve Barito.</p>\r\n<p>Cacan est arriv&eacute;e le 25 mars 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Septembre 2018</p>\r\n<p>Cacan va bien. Cacan est ensemble avec son amie Kiki Kalimantan dans une m&ecirc;me cage.</p>','FR'),
	(53513,650,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Cacan is a female gibbon of <em>Hylobates Agilis albibarbis</em>, one of gibbons species who live in Kalimantan, Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of his birth year : 2014.</p>\r\n<p>Cacan was saved in Bintang Linggi, Muara Teweh, Central Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>Cacan was arrived at Kalaweit on march, 25<sup>th</sup> 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>September 2018</p>\r\n<p>Cacan is doing well. She is active and eat well the fruits.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cacan is with another female gibbon name Kiki Kalimantan.</p>','EN'),
