	(53516,651,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Kiki est une femelle gibbon de l&rsquo;esp&egrave;ce <em>Hylobates muelleri muelleri</em>, l&rsquo;une des esp&egrave;ces de gibbons qui vit dans les sud &ndash; est de Born&eacute;o, approximativement dans le sud de la rivi&egrave;re Mahakam et &agrave; l&rsquo;ouest de la rivi&egrave;re Barito.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;estimation de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e de sa naissance : 2014.</p>\r\n<p>Kiki a &eacute;t&eacute; sauv&eacute;e &agrave; Bintang Linggi, un petit village qui se trouve sur le bord du fleuve Barito.</p>\r\n<p>Elle est arriv&eacute;e &agrave; Kalaweit le 25 mars 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Centre et Sanctuaire, Muara Teweh, Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>Septembre 2018</p>\r\n<p>Kiki va bien. Elle est toujours ensemble avec son amie Cacan.</p>','FR'),
	(53517,651,'DETAIL','HTML','2018-10-21 05:27:19',NULL,NULL,'<p>Kiki is a female gibbon of <em>Hylobates Muelleri muelleri</em>, one of gibbons species who can be found in southeast Kalimantan, approximately south of the Mahakam river and west of the Barito river.</p>\r\n<p>Estimation of her birth year : 2014.</p>\r\n<p>Kiki was saved in Bintang Linggi, a small village near our center at Muara Teweh.</p>\r\n<p>Kiki was arrived in Kalaweit on march, 25 2018.</p>\r\n<p>Notes :</p>\r\n<p>Pararawen Conservation Center and Santuary, Muara Teweh, Central Kalimantan.</p>\r\n<p>September 2018</p>\r\n<p>Kiki is doing well. She is always together with her friend Cacan.</p>','EN'),
